eap%20year%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsiblings-twins-triplets-born-on-leap-day%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELeap%20days%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20as%20rare%20as%20the%20Olympic%20games.%20So%2C%20being%20born%20on%20February%2029th%20is%20akin%20to%20being%20an%20Olympian%20%E2%80%94%20after%20all%2C%20every%20four%20years%2C%20both%20groups%20have%20their%20time%20in%20the%20spotlight.%20Only%20instead%20of%20breaking%20world%20records%20in%20the%20100-meter%20dash%2C%20I%20get%20texts%20from%20my%20friends%20that%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BHappy%20REAL%20birthday%2C%20nerd.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20was%20born%20on%20February%2029th%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20my%20birthday%20quickly%20became%20the%20butt%20of%20classmates'%20jokes.%20After%20all%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-birthday-freebies-and-discounts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eactual%20birthday%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20most%20years%20of%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20leap%20age%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhard-viral-test-questions-2017-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emath%20problem%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20classmates%20eager%20to%20solve.%20I've%20heard%20all%20the%20jokes.%20I%20would%20have%20to%20be%2064%20years%20old%20before%20I%20could%20drive%20because%2C%20at%2064%2C%20I%20would%20have%20had%2016%20leap%20birthdays.%20And%20for%20drinking%2C%20I%20would%20have%20to%20turn%2084%20before%20I%20would%20have%20celebrated%2021%20leap%20birthdays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20leap%20day%20birthday%20singled%20me%20out%20in%20a%20way%20that%20was%20entirely%20out%20of%20my%20control.%20To%20a%20kid%20who%20wanted%20to%20be%20as%20grown%20up%20as%20possible%2C%20having%20my%20age%20constantly%20divided%20by%20four%20got%20old%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAs%20an%20adult%2C%20I%20appreciate%20the%20uniqueness%20of%20my%20birthday%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20grew%20older%2C%20however%2C%20and%20after%20some%20prodding%20from%20family%20members%2C%20I%20began%20to%20realize%20what%20an%20opportunity%20I%20was%20given%2C%20and%20I%20started%20to%20embrace%20the%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpicked-son-baby-name-unique-no-longer-trendy-angry-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efun%20and%20unique%3C%2Fa%3E%20aspects%20of%20my%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20strove%20to%20celebrate%20my%20leap%20birthdays%20by%20partying%20in%20the%20fashion%20of%20my%20leap%20age.%20For%20my%2016th%20birthday%2C%20for%20example%2C%20we%20rented%20a%20reptile%20lady%20that%20comes%20to%20your%20home%20with%20a%20bunch%20of%20snakes%20%E2%80%94%20just%20as%20I%20did%20when%20I%20was%204.%20And%20I%20was%20just%20as%20terrified%20as%20when%20I%20was%204.%20Turning%20what%20was%20once%20a%20point%20of%20tension%20into%20a%20playful%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-does-the-royal-family-celebrate-birthdays-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebirthday%20tradition%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20also%20meant%20being%20able%20to%20more%20openly%20and%20frequently%20embrace%20my%20inner%20kid%2C%20rather%20than%20shying%20away%20from%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20feel%20pressure%20to%20celebrate%20big%20on%20leap%20years%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBirthdays%20come%20with%20stress%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bleaplings%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20people%20born%20on%20leap%20day%2C%20and%20yes%2C%20a%20classification%20that%20also%20sounds%20straight%20out%20of%20Tolkien%20lore%20%E2%80%94%20are%20far%20from%20immune.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideo-resurfaces-of-danny-masterson-genitals-joke-on-conan-obrien-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EConan%20O'Brien%3C%2Fa%3E%20once%20said%20of%20birthdays%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20like%20praise%20for%20something%20I%20didn't%20have%20anything%20to%20do%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20I%20generally%20fall%20in%20that%20same%20camp.%20Sometimes%2C%20birthday%20anxiety%20can%20loom%20even%20larger%20for%20leaplings%20since%20their%20%26quot%3Breal%26quot%3B%20birthday%20is%20less%20common.%20Every%20four%20years%2C%20pressure%20mounts%20to%20celebrate%20bigger%20or%20better%20than%20in%20non-leap%20years%20because%20leap%20birthdays%20are%20a%20scarce%20commodity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20always%20thought%20of%20my%20birthday%20as%20so%20arbitrary%20when%20I%20was%20growing%20up%20I%20hadn't%20given%20it%20a%20fair%20shake.%20Now%2C%20I%20take%20advantage%20of%20my%20leapling%20status%20whenever%20it%20benefits%20me.%20A%20remarkably%20supportive%20household%20means%20that%20on%20non-leap%20years%2C%20I%20can%20choose%20to%20celebrate%20on%20either%20February%2028th%20or%20March%201st.%20If%20the%20former%20happened%20to%20fall%20on%20Thursday%20and%20the%20latter%20happened%20to%20fall%20on%20Friday%2C%20then%20I%20was%20a%20March%20baby%20that%20year%20because%20a%20Friday%20birthday%20is%20more%20convenient%20than%20a%20Thursday%20one.%20Being%20able%20to%20pick%20and%20choose%20which%20day%20you%20celebrate%20is%20a%20perk%20unique%20to%20leaplings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.britannica.com%2Fscience%2FEgyptian-calendar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eancient%20Egyptians%20observed%20a%20365-day%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%20close.%20But%20without%20accounting%20for%20the%20extra%20five%20hours%2C%2048%20minutes%2C%20and%2046%20seconds%20of%20the%20solar%20year%2C%20they%20experienced%20a%20wandering%20calendar.%20After%20100%20years%2C%20the%20Egyptian%20calendar%20had%20not%20accounted%20for%20nearly%20twenty-five%20days%20%E2%80%94%20enough%20to%20alter%20agricultural%20timelines%2C%20keep%20corrupt%20leaders%20in%20office%2C%20and%20have%20tangible%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20I%20like%20to%20think%20of%20leap%20day%20babies%20as%20problem%20solvers.%20After%20all%2C%20without%20leap%20da