ote%20Ribakova.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESecondary%20sanctions%20are%20working%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-economy-chinese-banks-halt-payment-settlements-sanctions-chaozhou-commercial-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EChinese%20banks%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20tightening%20compliance%20checks%20with%20Russian%20businesses%20because%20they%20fear%20getting%20caught%20up%20in%20the%20West's%20increasingly%20restrictive%20sanctions%20against%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20include%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-takes-aim-financial-institutions-with-new-russia-sanctions-authority-2023-12-22%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esecondary%20sanctions%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20US%20authorized%20in%20December%2C%20which%20target%20financial%20institutions%20that%20help%20Russia%20skirt%20restrictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20of%20China's%20Big%20Four%20state%20banks%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-biggest-banks-stop-russia-payments-icbc-ccb-boc-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehalted%20payments%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20sanctioned%20Russian%20financial%20institutions%2C%20Russia's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiz.ru%2F1653256%2Fmariia-kolobova-milana-gadzhieva%2Fkomissiia-bez-perevoda-tri-krupneishikh-banka-knr-perestali-prinimat-platezhi-iz-rf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EIzvestia%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20news%20outlet%20reported%20on%20February%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Kremlin%20has%20acknowledged%20issues%20with%20Chinese%20bank%20transactions%2C%20with%20spokesperson%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barrons.com%2Fnews%2Frussia-admits-problems-with-china-payments-1d9e5887%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EDmitry%2