.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-istock-processed-food_6472960.jpg%3F20240229091947%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fultra-processed-foods-linked-to-32-physical-and-mental-health-problems-review-finds-13083503%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ultra-processed%20foods%20(UPFs)%20have%20been%20linked%20to%2032%20harmful%20health%20effects%2C%20including%20heart%20disease%2C%20type%202%20diabetes%2C%20cancer%20and%20mental%20health%20problems%2C%20according%20to%20the%20largest%20review%20into%20their%20impact.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fultra-processed-foods-linked-to-32-physical-and-mental-health-problems-review-finds-13083503%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fultra-processed-foods-linked-to-32-physical-and-mental-health-problems-review-finds-13083503%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fultra-processed-foods-linked-to-32-physical-and-mental-health-problems-review-finds-13083503%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Government%20Employees'%20Platform%20Plans%20Strike%20From%20May%201%20Over%20OPS%20Demand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F17212427%2FPurani-pension-lagu-karein.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20group%20of%20Union%20and%20state%20government%20employees%20announced%20they%20will%20go%20on%20indefinite%20strike%20starting%20on%20Labour%20Day%20(May%201)%20this%20year%20to%20demand%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20old%20pension%20scheme%20(OPS)%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Frestoration-of-old-pension-scheme-govt-employees-to-go-on-indefinite-strike-from-may-1%2Farticle67896754.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Joint%20Forum%20For%20Restoration%20of%20Old%20Pension%20Scheme%20(JFROPS)%2C%20which%20was%20described%20as%20a%20platform%20of%20trade%20unions%20and%20associations%20working%20among%20Union%20and%20state%20government%20employees%2C%20said%20it%20had%20decided%20to%20serve%20strike%20notices%20starting%20March%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20OPS%2C%20which%20was%20retired%20in%202004%2C%20retired%20government%20employees%20received%20half%20their%20last-drawn%20salary%20every%20month%20as%20a%20pension.%20The%20government%20concerned%20would%20foot%20the%20entire%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Pension%20Scheme%20(NPS)%20replaced%20the%20OPS%20and%20involves%20the%20employee%20contributing%2010%25%20of%20their%20basic%20salary%20and%20the%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findian-govt-likely-offer-assured-base-pensions-compromise-with-states-sources-2023-06-21%2F%5C%22%3Econtributing%2014%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20a%20corpus%2C%20which%20can%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fops-vs-nps-rbi-congress%5C%22%3Einvested%20into%20different%20types%20of%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20much%20an%20employee%20would%20receive%20upon%20retirement%20depends%20on%20the%20market%20return%20on%20these%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Gopal%20Mishra%2C%20who%20is%20convenor%20of%20the%20JFROPS%20and%20is%20among%20the%20leaders%20of%20a%20railway%20workers%E2%80%99%20union%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20go%20on%20strike%20was%20taken%20after%20talks%20with%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20broken%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20held%20several%20protests%20demanding%20restoration%20of%20OPS.%20We%20wrote%20letters%20to%20prime%20minister%20and%20finance%20minister%20urging%20them%20to%20restore%20the%20OPS.%20We%20have%20also%20been%20raising%20this%20issue%20in%20the%20JCM%20%5Bjoint%20consultative%20machinery%5D%20meetings%2C%20but%20the%20government%20ignored%20our%20demands%20and%20we%20are%20now%20forced%20to%20go%20on%20an%20indefinite%20strike%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mishra%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20cited%20government%20employees%E2%80%99%20unions%20as%20claiming%20that%20ahead%20of%20the%20call%20for%20a%20strike%2C%20ballots%20conducted%20in%20various%20government%20departments%20suggested%20that%20nearly%20100%25%20of%20employees%20supported%20a%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Funion-govt-employees-want-old-pension-scheme-restored%5C%22%3EProponents%20of%20restoring%20the%20OPS%20have%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20pension%20amounts%20under%20the%20NPS%20are%20%E2%80%9Cpaltry%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20the%20new%20scheme%20%E2%80%9Cis%20a%20disaster%20for%20the%20retiring%20employees%20in%20their%20old%20age%20and%20not%20a%20win-win%20situation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20also%20argued%20that%20pensioners%20were%20worse%20off%20under%20the%20NPS%20because%20it%20does%20not%20hike%20pensions%20on%20a%20regular%20basis%20in%20order%20to%20correct%20for%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20state%20governments%20have%20decided%20to%20restore%20the%20OPS%20for%20their%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20has%20said%20that%20going%20back%20to%20the%20OPS%20would%20increase%20governments%E2%80%99%20liabilities%20and%20put%20their%20financial%20security%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20said%20in%20parliament%20in%20December%20that%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-won-t-revert-to-old-pension-scheme-parliament-told-101702407420052.html%5C%22%3Edoes%20not%20plan%20on%20restoring%20the%20OPS%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F1054122%2Fcentral-government-employees-warned-against-participating-in-rally-to-demand-old-pension-scheme%5C%22%3Ewarned%20its%20employees%20from%20going%20on%20strike%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20and%20argued%20that%20their%20right%20to%20form%20associations%20did%20not%20include%20a%20guaranteed%20right%20to%20go%20on%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mishra%20was%20asked%20by%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20how%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20for%20the%20general%20elections%20would%20affect%20their%20planned%20strike%2C%20he%20said%20they%20wanted%20the%20issue%20to%20be%20discussed%20by%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20an%20issue%20that%20involves%20lives%20of%20crores%20of%20people.%20Let%20the%20people%20discuss%20and%20decide%20on%20our%20demands.%20Even%20if%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20comes%20in%20picture%2C%20the%20Cabinet%20will%20be%20there%2C%20the%20Cabinet%20secretary%20will%20be%20there%20and%20they%20can%20take%20a%20decision%20on%20our%20demand%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20employees%E2%80%99%20union%20leader%20was%20cited%20as%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%98all%20unions%E2%80%99%20except%20the%20pro-government%20Bharatiya%20Mazdoor%20Sangh%20would%20take%20part%20in%20their%20planned%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709197725000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F17212427%2FPurani-pension-lagu-karein.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fgovernment-employees-platform-plans-indefinite-strike-may-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shiv%20Gopal%20Mishra%2C%20convener%20of%20the%20Joint%20Forum%20For%20Restoration%20of%20Old%20Pension%20Scheme%2C%20said%20the%20decision%20to%20go%20on%20indefinite%20strike%20from%20May%201%20was%20taken%20after%20talks%20with%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20broken%20down.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fgovernment-employees-platform-plans-indefinite-stri