on%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Dilip%20Kumar%20(%40kmr_dilip)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkmr_dilip%2Fstatus%2F1762723872246313314%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2028%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20following%20post%2C%20the%20entrepreneur%20explained%20how%20one's%20health%20encompasses%20a%20broader%20spectrum%2C%20including%20physical%2C%20mental%20and%20social%20well-being%2C%20where%20the%20body's%20systems%20operate%20in%20harmony.%20%26quot%3BBeing%20fit%20is%20not%20equal%20to%20being%20healthy.%20Most%20people%20believe%20being%20healthy%20and%20being%20fit%20are%20one%20and%20the%20same.%20It's%20not.%20They%20are%20not%20synonymous%20and%20are%20distinct%20states%20of%20physical%20well-being%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kumar%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20fit%20means%20your%20ability%20to%20perform%20physical%20activities%20such%20as%20endurance%2C%20stamina%2C%20strength%2C%20flexibility%2C%20power%20%26amp%3B%20speed.%20These%20are%20a%20set%20of%20attributes%20that%20people%20have%20or%20develop%20to%20perform%20a%20physical%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fburger-singh-website-hacked-by-pakistani-group-company-responds-with-a-touch-of-humour-5148222%5C%22%3EBurger%20Singh%20Website%20Hacked%20By%20Pakistani%20Group%2C%20Company%20Responds%20With%20A%20Touch%20Of%20Humour%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20went%20on%20to%20debunk%20more%20misconceptions.%20%26quot%3BWe%20often%20look%20at%20athletes%20or%20movie%20stars%20as%20fit%20and%20healthy.%20But%20often%20they%20are%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BYou%20may%20be%20a%20runner%2C%20go%20to%20gym%20regularly%20or%20get%20your%20ten%20thousand%20daily%20steps.%20Fitness%20doesn't%20guarantee%20health.%20While%20being%20fit%20can%20contribute%