resigned%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmust-be-careful-of-rumours-mayawati-rejects-poll-alliance-reports-5085238%5C%22%3EMayawati%3C%2Fa%3E-led%20BSP%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP%20on%20February%2025.%20Reports%20suggest%20that%20three%20more%20BSP%20MPs%20are%20poised%20to%20follow%20suit%20before%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20with%20another%20BSP%20MP%20considering%20a%20switch%20to%20Jayant%20Chaudhary's%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20(RLD).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20Ghazipur%20MP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-revokes-bsp-leader-afzal-ansaris-disqualification-after-supreme-court-order-4844655%5C%22%3EAfzal%20Ansari%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20already%20secured%20a%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20ticket%20from%20the%20same%20seat%2C%20while%20Amroha%20MP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmp-danish-ali-abused-in-parliament-suspended-by-mayawati-from-party-for-anti-party-activities-4649152%23%3A~%3Atext%3DLok%2520Sabha%2520MP%2520Danish%2520Ali%2Cfor%2520the%2520action%2520against%2520him.%5C%22%3EDanish%20Ali%2C%20suspended%20by%20the%20BSP%20for%20anti-party%20activities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20set%20to%20join%20the%20Congress.%20Another%20BSP%20MP%20from%20Jaunpur%20joined%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20on%20February%2025.%20Consequently%2C%20out%20of%20a%20total%2010%20MPs%20in%202019%2C%20Mayawati's%20party%20may%20end%20up%20with%20retaining%20only%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20appears%20that%20BSP%20leaders%2C%20in%20a%20last-ditch%20effort%20to%20salvage%20their%20political%20futures%2C%20are%20fleeing%20to%20safer%20havens%2C%20leaving%20the%20once%20formidable%20party%20in%20a%20state%20of%20limbo.%20Following%20the%20seat%20pact%20between%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-bjp-should-not-ignore-sp-congress-alliance-5111410%5C%22%3ESP%20and%20the%20Congress%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20BSP%20leaders%20fear%20diminished%20electoral%20prospects%20as%20the%20contest%20shifts%20into%20a%20direct%20confrontation%20between%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20and%20the%20SP-Congress%20combine.%20Despite%20disappointment%20from%20both%20INDIA%20bloc%20parties%20and%20her%20own%20party%20leaders%2C%20Mayawati%20has%20remained%20steadfast%20in%20her%20stance%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-elections-mayawati-to-retire-from-politics-bsp-chief-responds-4865832%23%3A~%3Atext%3DBSP%2520president%2520Mayawati%2520on%2520Monday%2Cout%2520a%2520post%252Dpoll%2520alliance.%5C%22%3EBSP%20will%20contest%20the%20upcoming%20elections%20alone%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20notwithstanding%20its%20previous%20alliance%20with%20SP-RLD%20in%202019%2C%20which%20yielded%2010%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisconnect%20With%20People%20Behind%20The%20Decline%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSP's%20decline%20has%20been%20in%20the%20making%20for%20a%20long%20time%20now.%20In%20the%202007%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20party%20secured%20206%20seats%2C%20garnering%20over%2030%25%20of%20the%20votes.%20This%20success%20was%20largely%20attributed%20to%20Mayawati's%20ability%20to%20forge%20an%20unlikely%20alliance%20between%20Brahmins%20and%20Dalits%2C%20securing%20a%20majority.%20However%2C%20subsequent%20elections%20saw%20a%20steady%20decline%2C%20with%20the%20BSP%20winning%20only%2080%20seats%20in%202012%2C%20down%20to%2019%20in%202017%2C%20and%20finally%20just%20one%20in%202022%2C%20in%20the%20403-seat%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20assembly.%20In%202022%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20its%20vote%20share%20dropped%20to%20just%2012.88%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20BSP's%20fortunes%20mirrored%20this%20descent%2C%20plummeting%20from%2021%20seats%20in%202009%20to%20zero%20in%202014.%20The%20alliance%20with%20the%20SP-RLD%20in%202019%20provided%20a%20brief%20respite%2C%20resulting%20in%2010%20seats.%20Notably%2C%20its%20vote%20share%20remained%20consistent%20between%2019%25%20and%2021%25%20in%202014%20and%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EChanging%20Friendships%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERank%20opportunism%20and%20shrewd%20manoeuvres%20have%20defined%20Mayawati's%20political%20career.%20Riding%20on%20the%20promise%20of%20political%20empowerment%20for%20Dalits%2C%20Muslims%2C%20and%20other%20marginalised%20social%20groups%2C%20she%20served%20as%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20four%20times%2C%20aligning%20with%20different%20parties%20at%20different%20times.%20These%20electoral%20alliances%20were%20strategically%20formed%20to%20benefit%20the%20BSP%2C%20with%20tie-ups%20being%20discarded%20once%20they%20no%20longer%20served%20its%20interests.%20Even%20in%202019%2C%20Mayawati%20terminated%20the%20alliance%20with%20the%20SP's%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20her%20arch-rival%2C%20despite%20its%20electoral%20gains%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20BSP%20winning%20only%20one%20seat%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections%20while%20contesting%20alone.%20The%20SP%20in%20contrast%20got%20111%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20there%20is%20no%20denying%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20BSP%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20potent%20force%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20a%20minor%20player%20in%20the%20electoral%20arena%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20grave%20mistake%20to%20think%20that%20the%20party%20could%20be%20ignored.%20A%20party%20that%20still%20has%20around%2013%20per%20cent%20vote%20share%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20win%20many%20seats%20but%20it%20can%20definitely%20influence%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20polls%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Sanjay%20Pandey%2C%20a%20political%20analyst.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBSP's%20Loss%2C%20BJP's%20Gain%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20factors%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20BSP's%20slide.%20Firstly%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20succeeded%20in%20attracting%20Dalit%20voters%20on%20a%20large%20scale%20through%20its%20Hindutva%20agenda%20and%20various%20welfare%20schemes%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20disillusionment%20with%20the%20BSP.%20This%20disenchantment%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20smaller%20caste%20parties%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20(SBSP)%20and%20the%20Nishad%20Party%2C%20to%20eat%20into%20the%20BSP's%20base.%20The%20emergence%20of%20alternative%20Dalit%20leaders%2C%20such%20as%20Chandrashekhar's%20Azad%20Samaj%20Party%2C%20further%20fractured%20the%20BSP's%20support%20base.%20Leaders%20like%20O.P.%20Rajbhar%2C%20Dara%20Singh%20Chauhan%20and%20Swami%20Prasad%20Maurya%20left%20in%20search%20of%20greener%20pastures%2C%20significantly%20denting%20the%20BSP's%20core%20support%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslim%20voters%2C%20too%2C%20have%20oscillated%20between%20loyalty%20to%20the%20SP%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20perceiving%20these%20parties%20as%20better-equipped%20to%20challenge%20the%20BJP.%20The%20BSP's%20decision%20to%20contest%20alone%20further%20diminishes%20its%20appeal%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20shift%20of%20Muslim%20votes%20to%20the%20SP-Congress%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDalit%20vote%20of%20the%20BSP%20will%20mainly%20shift%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Muslims%20may%20move%20to%20the%20SP-Congress%20alliance%20as%20there%20is%20no%20third%20alternative.%20Though%20BSP%20may%20not%20be%20in%20a%20winning%20position%2C%20it%20will%20still%20try%20to%20keep%20its%20vote%20share%20intact%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20J.P.%20Shukla%2C%20a%20senior%20political%20analyst%20based%20in%20Lucknow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20'Third%20Party'%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20many%20alleged%20corruption%20cases%20pending%20against%20her%2C%20Mayawati%20has%20adopted%20a%20guarded%20approach%20as%20far%20as%20her%20politics%20is%20concerned.%20For%20the%20BJP%2C%20it%20suits%20to%20use%20the%20BSP%20as%20the%20'third%20party'%20to%20turn%20the%20battle%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20into%20a%20triangular%20one.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20will%20also%20want%20to%20see%20that%20the%20BSP%20remains%20in%20the%20fight%20in%20at%20least%20Muslim-dominant%20constituencies%2C%26quot%3B%20adds%20Shukla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20upcoming%20general%20elections%20are%20poised%20to%20be%20a%20two-party%20contest%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20SP-Congress%20alliance.%20With%20Dalits%20increasingly%20gravitating%20towards%20the%20BJP%20over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20the%20BSP%20might%20not%20be%20averse%20to%20subtle%20collaboration%20with%20the%20party.%20The%20BJP's%20Jatav%20support%20base%20has%20surged%20from%205%25%20in%202012%20to%2021%25%20in%202022%2C%20while%20its%20non-Jatav%20base%20has%20expanded%20from%2011%25%20in%202012%20to%2041%25%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20BSP%20has%20rebuffed%20overtures%20from%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20bloc%20thus%20far%2C%20in%20politics%2C%20nothing%20is%20definitive.%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20with%20its%20size%20and%20complexity%2C%20promises%20an%20engaging%20battle%20in%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709196240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fja6ma2tk_mayawati-pti_625x300_21_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-looming-irrelevance-of-the-bahujan-samaj-party-bsp-5149198%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BSP%20leaders%2C%20in%20a%20last-ditch%20effort%20to%20salvage%20their%20political%20futures%2C%20are%20fleeing%20to%20safer%20havens%2C%20leaving%20the%20once%20formidable%20party%20in%20a%20state%20of%20deep%20limbo.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv