e.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F29135301%2FScreenshot-2024-02-29-at-1.52.52-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Law%20Commission%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Flaw-panel-likely-to-recommend-new-chapter-on-one-nation-one-poll-in-constitution-2-2913909%5C%22%3Eis%20likely%20to%20recommend%20adding%20a%20new%20chapter%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20constitution%20on%20%E2%80%98one%20nation%2C%20one%20election%E2%80%99%20to%20aid%20simultaneous%20polls%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20state%20assemblies%20and%20local%20bodies%20by%202029%2C%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EHerald%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20suggested%20amendment%20to%20the%20Constitution%20would%20introduce%20a%20new%20chapter%20covering%20issues%20related%20to%20simultaneous%20elections%2C%20their%20sustainability%2C%20and%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20common%20electoral%20roll.%20This%20chapter%2C%20if%20adopted%2C%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Flaw-panel-likely-to-recommend-new-chapter-on-one-nation-one-poll-in-constitution-2-2913909%5C%22%3Ehold%20the%20authority%20to%20override%20other%20constitutional%20provisions%3C%2Fa%3E%20concerning%20the%20terms%20of%20legislative%20assemblies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20commission%2C%20led%20by%20Justice%20(retd)%20Ritu%20Raj%20Awasthi%2C%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20recommend%20synchronization%20of%20polls%20in%20three%20phases%20over%20the%20five-year%20period.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20commission%20will%20recommend%20that%20the%20first%20phase%20may%20deal%20with%20state%20assemblies%20whose%20period%20will%20have%20to%20be%20curtailed%20by%20a%20few%20months%20%E2%80%93%20three%20or%20six%20months%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20event%20of%20a%20government%20collapse%20due%20to%20a%20vote%20of%20no%20confidence%20or%20a%20hung%20House%2C%20the%20Law%20Commission%20proposes%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cunity%20government%E2%80%9D%20comprising%20representatives%20from%20various%20political%20parties.%20If%20this%20approach%20proves%20ineffective%2C%20the%20recommendation%20is%20to%20conduct%20fresh%20elections%20for%20the%20remaining%20term%20of%20the%20House.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fone-nation-one-election-one-leader-one-faith-one-business-house%5C%22%3EOne%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%2C%20One%20Leader%2C%20One%20Faith%2C%20One%20Business%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSuppose%20fresh%20elections%20are%20called%20for%20and%20the%20government%20still%20has%20three%20years%2C%20then%20polls%20should%20be%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20term%20%E2%80%93%20three%20years%20%E2%80%93%20to%20ensure%20sustainability%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20source%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Flaw-panel-likely-to-recommend-new-chapter-on-one-nation-one-poll-in-constitution-2-2913909%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20paper%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimultaneously%2C%20a%20high-level%20committee%2C%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20former%20President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%2C%20is%20also%20working%20on%20a%20report%20exploring%20the%20feasibility%20of%20simultaneous%20polls%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20are%20expected%20to%20take%20place%20in%20April-May%2C%20state%20polls%20for%20Maharashtra%2C%20Haryana%20and%20Jharkhand%20are%20expected%20later%20this%20year.%20These%20will%20be%20followed%20by%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eelections%20in%20Bihar%20and%20Delhi%20next%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20Assam%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20T