tent%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ishan%20Kishan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107047-ishan-kishan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIshan%20Kishan%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64384-shreyas-santosh-iyer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20on%20Wednesday%20omitted%20from%20BCCI's%20Annual%20Player%20Contracts%20for%20Team%20India%20(Senior%20Men)%20for%20the%202023-24%20season%20(October%201st%2C%202023%20to%20September%2030th%2C%202024).%20Despite%20featuring%20regularly%20in%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20in%20recent%20times%2C%20the%20duo's%20sacking%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20strong%20message%20by%20the%20BCCI%20for%20those%20who%20are%20ignoring%20domestic%20cricket.%20While%20Ishan%20Kishan%20was%20last%20part%20of%20the%20Test%20squad%20during%20India's%20Tour%20of%20South%20Africa%20in%20December%2C%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20played%20the%20first%20two%20Tests%20of%20the%20ongoing%20series%20against%20England.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20the%20BCCI%20removed%20the%20two%20senior%20player%20from%20the%20contracts%20list.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20BCCI%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20single%20out%20the%20duo's%20absence%20with%20the%20following%20line%20in%20the%20list%3A%20%26quot%3BPlease%20note%20that%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20and%20Ishan%20Kishan%20were%20not%20considered%20for%20the%20annual%20contracts%20in%20this%20round%20of%20recommendations.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fshreyas-iyer-and-ishan-kishan-snubbed-as-bcci-announce-new-player-central-contracts-9186055%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20sacking%20from%20the%20BCCI%20central%20contract%20list%20makes%20the%20chances%20of%20the%20duo%20bleak%20for%20the%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20are%20senior%20members%20of%20their%20respective%20sides%20in%20%C2%A0the%20IPL.%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20is%20expected%20to%20lead%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20while%20Ishan%20Kishan%20will%20play%20for%20Mumbai%20Indians.%20However%2C%20the%20report%20added%20that%20there%20is%20a%20chance%20that%20they%20would%20be%20considered%20for%20national%20team%20selection%20only%20of%20they%20feature%20in%20domestic%20cricket.%20%E2%80%9CIshan%20was%20granted%20a%20break%20that%20he%20sought.%20But%20he%20hasn't%20reported%20to%20the%20NCA%20or%20the%20state%20unit%2C%20but%20continues%20to%20train%20alone.%20Under%20the%20circumstances%2C%20there%20was%20no%20chance%20for%20the%20BCCI%20to%20offer%20a%20central%20contract.%20Similarly%20with%20Shreyas%2C%20we%20went%20by%20the%20medical%20reports.%20The%20door%20is%20still%20open%20for%20them%20provided%20they%20play%20domestic%20cricket%20regularly%2C%E2%80%9D%20sources%20in%20the%20know%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20was%20no%20official%20reason%20given%20on%20why%20Ishan%20Kishan%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20were%20dropped%2C%20one%20line%20in%20BCCI's%20release%20gives%20a%20strong%20hint.%20%26quot%3BThe%20BCCI%20has%20recommended%20that%20all%20athletes%20give%20precedence%20to%20participating%20in%20domestic%20cricket%20during%20periods%20when%20they%20are%20not%20representing%20the%20national%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BCCI%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ishan%20Kishan%20had%20left%20India's%20Tour%20of%20South%20Africa%2C%20the%20BCCI%20had%20said%20on%20December%2017%3A%20%26quot%3BMr%20Ishan%20Kishan%20has%20requested%20the%20BCCI%20to%20be%20released%20from%20the%20upcoming%20Test%20series%20against%20South%20Africa%20citing%20personal%20reasons.%20The%20wicket-keeper%20has%20subsequently%20been%20withdrawn%20from%20the%20Test%20squad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20was%20expected%20that%20Ishan%20Kishan%20would%20p