e%20nation%20speech%2C%20the%20Russian%20president%20says%20his%20military%20is%20succeeding%20in%20Ukraine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A80%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Flive%2Fworld-europe-68431017%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20Can't%20Be%20Held%20Guilty%20For%20Abetment%20Of%20Wife's%20Suicide%20Unless...%3A%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20man%20cannot%20be%20held%20guilty%20for%20abetment%20of%20his%20wife's%20suicide%20within%20seven%20years%20of%20marriage%20unless%20there%20is%20cogent%20evidence%20of%20harassment%20or%20cruelty%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20said%20while%20acquitting%20a%20man%20charged%20with%20abetting%20the%20suicide%20of%20his%20wife%20three%20decades%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%20113A%20of%20the%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%20establishes%20the%20presumption%20of%20abetment%20by%20a%20husband%20and%20in-laws%20in%20cases%20where%20a%20woman's%20suicide%20occurs%20within%20seven%20years%20of%20marriage%20and%20she%20has%20been%20subjected%20to%20cruelty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20case%2C%20the%20man%20got%20married%20in%201992.%20The%20prosecution%20claimed%20that%20soon%20after%20marriage%2C%20the%20man%20and%20his%20parents%20started%20demanding%20money%20as%20he%20wanted%20to%20start%20a%20ration%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecords%20reveal%20that%20on%20November%2019%2C%201993%2C%20the%20woman%20committed%20suicide%20by%20consuming%20poison.%20According%20to%20the%20prosecution%2C%20she%20committed%20suicide%20on%20account%20of%20incessant%20harassment%20at%20the%20end%20of%20her%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20sessions%20judge%20of%20Karnal%20in%201998%20held%20the%20man%20guilty%20of%20the%20offence%20punishable%20under%20Section%20306%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20which%20was%20upheld%20by%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20that%20to%20convict%20a%20person%20under%20Section%20306%20(abetment%20of%20suicide)%20of%20the%20IPC%2C%20there%20has%20to%20be%20a%20clear%20%26quot%3Bmens%20rea%26quot%3B%20(criminal%20intent)%20to%20commit%20the%20offence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justice%20J%20B%20Pardiwala%20and%20Justice%20Manoj%20Misra%20said%20mere%20harassment%20is%20not%20sufficient%20to%20hold%20an%20accused%20guilty%20of%20abetting%20the%20commission%20of%20suicide%20and%20it%20also%20requires%20an%20active%20act%20or%20direct%20act%20which%20led%20the%20person%20to%20commit%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20said%20courts%20must%20remain%20very%20careful%20and%20vigilant%20in%20applying%20the%20correct%20principles%20of%20law%20governing%20the%20subject%20of%20abetment%20of%20suicide%20of%20a%20woman%20within%20seven%20years%20of%20marriage%20or%20it%20may%20give%20an%20impression%20that%20the%20conviction%20is%20not%20legal%20but%20rather%20moral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20court%20has%20held%20that%20from%20the%20mere%20fact%20of%20suicide%20within%20seven%20years%20of%20marriage%2C%20one%20should%20not%20jump%20to%20the%20conclusion%20of%20abetment%20unless%20cruelty%20was%20proved.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20cogent%20evidence%20of%20harassment%20or%20cruelty%2C%20an%20accused%20cannot%20be%20held%20guilty%20for%20the%20offence%20under%20Section%20306%20of%20IPC%20by%20raising%20a%20presumption%20under%20Section%20113A%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20mere%20demand%20of%20money%20from%20the%20wife%20or%20her%20parents%20for%20running%20a%20business%20without%20anything%20more%20would%20not%20constitute%20cruelty%20or%20harassment.%20The%20top%20court%20also%20said%20that%20from%20the%20mere%20fact%20of%20suicide%20within%20seven%20years%20of%20marriage%2C%20one%20should%20not%20jump%20to%20the%20conclusion%20of%20abetment%20unless%20cruelty%20was%20proven.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHad%20there%20been%20any%20clinching%20evidence%20of%20incessant%20harassment%20on%20account%20of%20which%20the%20wife%20was%20left%20with%20no%20other%20option%20but%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20her%20life%2C%20it%20could%20have%20been%20said%20that%20the%20accused%20intended%20the%20consequences%20of%20his%20act%2C%20namely%2C%20suicide%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20courts%20should%20be%20extremely%20careful%20in%20assessing%20evidence%20under%20section%20113A%20to%20find%20out%20if%20cruelty%20was%20meted%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it%20transpires%20that%20a%20victim%20committing%20suicide%20was%20hypersensitive%20to%20ordinary%20petulance%2C%20discord%20and%20differences%20in%20domestic%20life%20quite%20common%20to%20the%20society%20to%20which%20the%20victim%20belonged%20and%20such%20petulance%2C%20discord%20and%20differences%20were%20not%20expected%20to%20induce%20a%20similarly%20circumstanced%20individual%20in%20a%20given%20society%20to%20commit%20suicide%2C%20the%20conscience%20of%20the%20court%20would%20not%20be%20satisfied%20for%20holding%20that%20the%20accused%20charged%20of%20abetting%20the%20offence%20of%20suicide%20was%20guilty%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20ordeal%20suffered%20by%20the%20man%2C%20the%20top%20court%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bcriminal%20justice%20system%20of%20ours%20can%20itself%20be%20a%20punishment%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20exactly%20what%20has%20happened%20in%20this%20case.%20It%20did%20not%20take%20more%20than%2010%20minutes%20for%20this%20court%20to%20reach%20an%20inevitable%20conclusion%20that%20the%20conviction%20of%20the%20appellant%20convict%20for%20the%20offence%20punishable%20under%20Section%20306%20of%20the%20IPC%20is%20not%20sustainable%20in%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ordeal%20for%20the%20appellant%20started%20sometime%20in%201993%20and%20is%20coming%20to%20an%20end%20in%202024%2C%20i.e.%20almost%20after%20a%20period%20of%2030%20years%20of%20suffering.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20are%20also%20mindful%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20young%20woman%20died%20leaving%20behind%20her%20six-month-old%20infant.%20No%20crime%20should%20go%20unpunished.%20But%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20guilt%20of%20the%20accused%20has%20to%20be%20determined%20in%20accordance%20with%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Cthead%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Cth%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3EHelplines%3C%2Fth%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Fthead%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EVandrevala%20Foundation%20for%20Mental%20Health%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B919999666555%5C%22%3E9999666555%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%5C%22%3Ehelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3ETISS%20iCall%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B912225521111%5C%22%3E022-25521111%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Monday-Saturday%3A%208%20am%20to%2010%20pm)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%20%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E(If%20you%20need%20support%20or%20know%20someone%20who%20does%2C%20please%20reach%20out%20to%20your%20nearest%20mental%20health%20specialist.)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709193720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-02%2Fa1ooga8_supreme-court-of-india_650x400_14_February_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-cant-be-held-guilty-for-abetment-of-wifes-suicide-unless-cogent-evidence-exists-supreme-court-5148989%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20man%20cannot%20be%20held%20guilty%20for%20abetment%20of%20his%20wife's%20suicide%20within%20seven%20years%20of%20marriage%20unless%20there%20is%20co