d%20Demolition%20Matter%20Referred%20to%20Heritage%20Committee'%3A%20Police%20to%20HC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F27145840%2Fimage-1676.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Delhi%20Traffic%20Police%20on%20Wednesday%20(February%2028)%20told%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20that%20the%20matter%20concerning%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20150-year-old%20Sunehri%20Bagh%20mosque%20has%20been%20referred%20to%20the%20heritage%20conservation%20committee%20(HCC)%20of%20the%20urban%20development%20ministry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20New%20Delhi%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(NDMC)%20in%20December%20had%20issued%20a%20public%20notice%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20medieval%20era%20mosque%20after%20they%20received%20references%20from%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20traffic%20police%20to%20%E2%80%9Censure%20sustainable%20mobility%E2%80%9D%20of%20vehicles%20in%20the%20area.%20The%20NDMC%20then%20sought%20public%20opinion%20on%20the%20proposed%20removal%20of%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20notice%20had%20come%20shortly%20after%20the%20high%20court%20had%20dismissed%20a%20plea%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Waqf%20Board%20(DWB)%20that%20sought%20to%20restrain%20NDMC%20from%20demolishing%20or%20altering%20parts%20of%20the%20heritage%20structure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20court%20was%20addressing%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20Abdul%20Aziz%2C%20the%20mosque%E2%80%99s%20imam%2C%20challenging%20this%20notice.%20Aziz%20argued%20that%20the%20notice%20was%20issued%20with%20malafide%20intention%20and%20lacked%20any%20evidence%20or%20research%20demonstrating%20traffic%20congestion%20due%20to%20the%20mosque%E2%80%99s%20presence%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fdelhi-news%2Freferred-sunehri-bagh-matter-to-heritage-panel-police-to-delhi-hc-101709143215151.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20court%20proceedings%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Sanjay%20Jain%2C%20representing%20the%20traffic%20police%2C%20informed%20the%20bench%20that%20the%20petition%20challenging%20the%20NDMC%20notice%20had%20effectively%20resolved%20itself.%20This%20was%20because%20the%20matter%20had%20been%20referred%20to%20HCC%20following%20the%20consideration%20of%20public%20opinions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAziz%20and%20DWB%2C%20represented%20by%20advocate%20Viraj%20Datar%20and%20senior%20advocate%20Sanjoy%20Ghose%2C%20maintained%20that%20the%20notice%20was%20contested%20on%20grounds%20of%20competence%2C%20emphasising%20that%20it%20could%20not%20have%20been%20issued%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20law.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmosque-on-govts-demolition-radar-has-ties-to-indias-constituent-assembly%5C%22%3EMosque%20on%20Govt%E2%80%99s%20Demolition%20Radar%20Has%20Ties%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20Constituent%20Assembly%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20NDMC%2C%20through%20advocate%20Shriharsha%20Peechara%2C%20had%20assured%20the%20court%20that%20no%20action%20would%20be%20taken%20until%20HCC%20makes%20a%20final%20decision.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20decision%20has%20to%20be%20taken%20by%20the%20HCC%2C%20not%20by%20us%E2%80%A6%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20even%20touch%20a%20brick%20without%20HCCs%20permission%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fdelhi-news%2Freferred-sunehri-bagh-matter-to-heritage-panel-police-to-delhi-hc-101709143215151.html%5C%22%3EPeechara%20had%20submitted%20before%20the%20bench.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20high%20court%20had%20refused%20to%20entertain%20a%20plea%20filed%20by%20the%20Waqf%20Welfare%20Forum%20seeking%20a%20similar%20relief%2C%20the%20paper%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBacklash%20on%20NDMC%E2%80%99s%20move%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20History%20Congress%20(IHC)%2C%20national%20level%20organisation%20of%20historians%2C%20had%20called%20the%20NDMC%E2%80%99s%20decision%20%E2%80%9Cunacceptable%20and%20unwise%E2%80%9D%20and%20said%20that%20there%20has%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fconstant-attempt-to-erode-medieval-architecture-heritage-historians-org-on-sunehri-bagh-mosque%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cconstant%20attempt%20to%20erode%20our%20medieval%20architectural%20heritage%20in%20recent%20times%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20resolution%20passed%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CApart%20from%20its%20intrinsic%20importance%20as%20a%20relic%20from%20an%20era%20of%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20history%2C%20its%20subsequent%20history%20during%20the%20construction%20of%20New%20Delhi%20is%20also%20of%20relevance.%20Its%20location%20on%20the%20roundabout%20is%20evocative%20of%20the%20town%20plan%20of%20New%20Delhi%20which%20sought%20to%20incorporate%20many%20historic%20structures%2C%20particularly%20those%20in%20active%20use%20as%20features%20of%20the%20new%20city%20plan%20instead%20of%20demolishing%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20proposal%20to%20remove%20the%20roundabout%20is%20unacceptable%20and%20an%20unwise%20modification%20of%20an%20important%20feature%20of%20the%20street%20plan%20of%20New%20Delhi%20of%20which%20roundabouts%20are%20an%20integral%20and%20essential%20feature%2C%E2%80%9D%20IHC%E2%80%99s%20resolution%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20mosque%20had%20also%20earned%20Heritage%20III%20status%20for%20its%20historical%20significance%20in%202009.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSunehri%20Bagh%20Masjid%20is%20not%20just%20a%20mosque%2C%20it%20has%20a%20history%20that%20is%20closely%20associated%20with%20several%20of%20our%20freedom%20fighters.%20Hasrat%20Mohani%2C%20member%20of%20our%20Constituent%20Assembly%20used%20to%20stay%20here%20while%20attending%20the%20meetings.%20Care%20for%20its%20illustrious%20history%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20historian%20S.%20Irfan%20Habib%20on%20X.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709189384000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F27145840%2Fimage-1676.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsunehri-bagh-masjid-demolition-matter-referred-to-heritage-committee-police-to-hc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20court%20was%20addressing%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20Abdul%20Aziz%2C%20the%20mosque's%20imam%2C%20challenging%20NDMC's%20notice%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20medieval%20era%20mosque%20to%20'alleviate%20traffic'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsunehri-bagh-masjid-demolition-matter-referred-to-heritage-committee-police-to-hc%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20affected%20or%20consumed%20by%20trolls%3B%20Kareena%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709189170000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108096560%2Cimgsize-30342.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkareena-kapoor-khan-on-social-media-trolls-i-dont-get-affected-or-consumed-by-it%2Farticleshow%2F108096646.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108096646.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%20addresses%20the%20issue%20of%20negativity%20on%20social%20media%2C%20emphasizing%20the%20importance%20of%20happiness%20and%20mental%20well-being.%20She%20talks%20about%20managing%20her%20online%20presence%2