r%20Advisory%20Services%20(IiAS)%20have%20recommended%20not%20to%20support%20Manju%20Agarwal%E2%80%99s%20re-appointment%20as%20an%20independent%20director%20in%20CMS%20Info%20Systems%2C%20on%20account%20of%20her%20poor%20track%20record%20on%20the%20board%20of%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank.%20The%20SES%20report%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20is%20scathing%20on%20her%20performance%20at%20the%20bank.%20The%20report%20comments%20on%20her%20performance%20in%20the%20light%20of%20the%20prior%20regulatory%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20is%2C%20what%20did%20she%20do%3F%20Did%20she%20use%20her%20experience%20in%20resolving%20the%20issue%3F%20The%20answer%20is%20No.%20The%20problems%20persisted%20and%20culminated%20in%20the%20death%20warrant%20for%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank.%20Were%20her%20suggestions%20ignored%3F%20Possibly%2C%20but%20if%20she%20can%20resign%20now%20%5B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bseindia.com%2Fxml-data%2Fcorpfiling%2FAttachHis%2F732ff8a8-f500-4d8e-91c7-23041884c994.pdf%5C%22%3Elink%3C%2Fa%3E%5D%2C%20she%20could%20have%20done%20it%20long%20back%2C%20thus%20bringing%20fault%20lines%20of%20the%20bank%20in%20open%20and%20would%20have%20saved%20not%20only%20problems%20faced%20by%20stakeholders%20but%20for%20herself%2C%20as%20SES%20views%20this%20as%20loss%20of%20reputation%20for%20her%20after%20a%20chequered%20career%20at%20the%20premier%20bank.%20Thus%2C%20SES%20concludes%20that%20she%20did%20not%20adhere%20to%20the%20code%20of%20conduct%20as%20envisaged%20and%20failed%20in%20protecting%20the%20institution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20fate%20will%20rightly%20befall%20all%20the%20other%20independent%20directors%20at%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20during%20FY23%20when%20their%20terms%20come%20up%20for%20re-appointment%20or%20if%20they%20are%20mistakenly%20selected%20for%20their%20%E2%80%9Cexpertise%20and%20experience%E2%80%9D%20as%20directors%20in%20other%20companies.%20There%20are%20consequences%20for%20independent%20directors%20who%20sit%20on%20boards%20while%20turning%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20repeated%20regulatory%20lapses%20and%20sending%20their%20resignations%20immediately%2C%20prior%20or%20post%20stringent%20regulatory%20action%20to%20possibly%20save%20their%20reputation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20directorships%20held%20by%20individuals%20who%20were%20independent%20directors%20of%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20in%20FY22%20and%20FY23%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22209%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmanju-agarwal-aa7258a8%2Fdetails%2Fexperience%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EManju%20Agarwal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22189%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fshinjini-kumar-a7b14020%2F%3ForiginalSubdomain%3Din%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShinjini%20Kumar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22169%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cyient.com%2Fboard-of-directors%2Framesh-abhishek%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERamesh%20Abhishek%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22209%5C%22%3EGulf%20Oil%20Lubricants%20India%20Ltd%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22189%5C%22%3EBOB%20BNP%20Asset%20Management%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22169%5C%22%3ECyient%20Ltd.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22209%5C%22%3EHinduja%20Leyland%20Finance%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22189%5C%22%3ECGAP%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22169%5C%22%3E%E2%80%93%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22209%5C%22%3EPolycab%20India%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22189%5C%22%3ENium%20Forex%20Private%20Ltd.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22169%5C%22%3E%E2%80%93%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22209%5C%22%3EGlenmark%20Life%20Sciences%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22189%5C%22%3E%E2%80%93%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22169