at-express-delayed-as-dense-fog-engulfs-north-india-check-full-list-article-106745376%5C%22%3Ea%20dozen%20trains%20running%20late%20by%20even%20eight%20to%2010%20hours%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20has%20further%20been%20reported%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.magzter.com%2Fstories%2FNewspaper%2FThe-Free-Press-Journal%2FVande-Bharat-Costs-237-More-Than-Shatabdi-RTI-Reveals%5C%22%3EVande%20Bharat%20is%202.5%20times%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20Shatabdi%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20that%20for%20around%20480%20bogeys%20of%20the%20Vande%20Bharat%20there%20could%20have%20been%20more%20than%201%2C000%20bogeys%20of%20Shatabdi%20trains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%2C%20however%2C%20not%20discussed%20is%20the%20inhuman%20form%20of%20inherently%20ordained%20structure%20leading%20to%20the%20exploitation%20of%20the%20people%20who%20are%20responsible%20for%20providing%20basic%20services%20in%20the%20Vande%20Bharat%20trains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELong%20duty%20hours%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2015%2C%202024%2C%20the%20Vande%20Bharat%20train%20which%20started%20at%206%20am%20from%20Varanasi%20reached%20Delhi%20late.%20Instead%20of%20its%20scheduled%20departure%20at%203%20pm%2C%20it%20left%20the%20national%20capital%20at%205%20pm.%20The%20expected%20time%20of%20arrival%20at%20Varanasi%20in%20the%20return%20journey%20is%2011%20pm%2C%20however%2C%20it%20reached%20the%20next%20day%20at%205%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20527px)%2085vw%2C%20527px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27162355%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-27-at-4.10.25-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22527%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27162355%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-27-at-4.10.25-PM.png%20440w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27162355%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-27-at-4.10.25-PM-300x225.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-699125%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22395%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EInside%20a%20Vande%20Bharat%20train.%20Photo%3A%20Tikender%20Singh%20Panwar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20set%20of%20people%2C%20including%20the%20regular%20train%20staff%2C%20outsourced%20staff%20providing%20services%20like%20serving%20food%2C%20and%20sanitation%2C%20travel%20back%20by%20the%20same%20train.%20They%20normally%20get%20a%20break%20of%20just%20six%20hours.%20The%20staff%2C%20excluding%20the%20regular%20staff%20who%20are%20mainly%20ticket%20checkers%20given%20alternative%20duties%2C%20boards%20the%20train%20back%20to%20Delhi%20from%20Varanasi%20and%20the%20rhythm%20continues%20till%20they%20get%20a%20day%E2%80%99s%20break%2C%20when%20the%20train%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2015%2C%20the%20staff%20appeared%20to%20have%20been%20on%20duty%20for%20more%20than%2024%20hours%20without%20any%20rest%20and%20without%20any%20economic%20benefit%20like%20over%20time%2C%20etc.%20It%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20curiosity%20whether%20this%20happens%20to%20all%20the%20Vande%20Bharat%20trains%20where%20the%20staff%20are%20made%20to%20work%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20working%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20for%20simple%20understanding%20if%20the%20train%20runs%20on%20time%20(even%20though%20in%20many%20cases%20it%20does%20not)%20the%20duty%20hours%20are%20more%20than%2016%20hours%20per%20day%2C%20per%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fvande-bharat-express-delhi-katra%5C%22%3EVande%20Bharat%20Express%3A%20What%E2%80%99s%20in%20a%20Name%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIncome%20issues%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20much%20money%20is%20paid%20to%20the%20staff%3F%20How%20do%20they%20manage%20their%20rest%20or%20bodily%20requirements%3F%20Where%20do%20they%20take%20rest%20or%20sleep%3F%20Are%20they%20being%20provided%20with%20some%20social%20housing%20or%20hostels%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20an%20average%2C%20the%20Vande%20Bharat%20workers%20this%20author%20spoke%20to%20suggested%20that%20one%20such%20train%20has%20a%20staff%20of%20over%2040%20people%20as%20service%20workers%20and%20around%2010-12%20as%20sanitation%20workers%20and%20the%20same%20number%20of%20ticket-checking%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outsourced%20workers%2C%20this%20author%20learnt%2C%20are%20paid%20a%20sum%20of%20around%20Rs%2012%2C000%20per%20month%20with%20no%20overtime.%20The%20sanitation%20workers%20are%20paid%20Rs%2010%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20sum%2C%20on%20an%20average%2C%20they%20work%20120%20hours%20a%20week%2C%20averaging%2020%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20and%20around%20480%20hours%20a%20month%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20to%20Varanasi%20train%20one%20side%20journey%20is%20eight%20hours%20and%20the%20train%20is%20late%20by%20almost%20two%20hours%20on%20an%20average%2C%20the%20travel%20time%20and%20the%20time%20they%20take%20in%20preparing%20the%20train%20roughly%20comes%20to%20around%2019-20%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBasic%20provisions%20like%20Employees%20State%20Insurance%20(ESI)%2C%20provident%20fund%2C%20etc.%2C%20were%20not%20heard%20of%20by%20the%20workers%20serving%20in%20the%20train%20in%20which%20the%20author%20travelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInherently%20flawed%20design%20of%20the%20contract%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20567px)%2085vw%2C%20567px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27162610%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-27-at-4.09.44-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22567%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27162610%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-27-at-4.09.44-PM.png%20444w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27162610%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-27-at-4.09.44-PM-300x198.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-699126%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22374%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EVande%20Bharat%20train%20from%20Delhi%20to%20Varanasi.%20Photo%3A%20Tikender%20Singh%20Panwar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20railway%20ministry%20and%20particularly%20the%20current%20government%20must%20realise%20that%20such%20a%20model%20of%20development%20and%20generating%20employment%20is%20not%20only%20faulty%20but%20also%20unsustainable.%20Instead%20of%20providing%20regular%20employment%20to%20the%20workforce%2C%20the%20government%20itself%20is%20promoting%20informality%20and%20accentuating%20the%20vagaries%20of%20the%20current%20ecosystem%20that%20is%20based%20on%20squeezing%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20marginalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20massive%20drive%20for%20redevelopment%20of%20railway%20stations%20and%20allowing%20private%20operators%20to%20grab%20these%20contracts%20are%20not%20need%20based%2C%20rather%20they%20are%20more%20to%20build%20infrastructure%20that%20is%20not%20based%20on%20any%20substantive%20requirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20such%20an%20infrastructure%20is%20considered%20necessary%20the%20government%20should%20not%20shirk%20from%20its%20responsibility%20of%20providing%20decent%20work%20conditions%20to%20the%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20the%20government%20needs%20to%20do%20is%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20huge%20workforce%20that%20the%20railways%20employ%20and%20make%20it%20sustainable%20with%20some%20of%20the%20essentials%20of%20sustainable%20development%20goals%20including%20better%20livelihoods.%20If%20the%20government%20itself%20is%20negating%20such%20a%20principle%2C%20one%20can%20imagine%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20other%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minimum%20that%20the%20railways%20should%20do%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20tenders%20floated%20for%20such%20services%20do%20not%20just%20lead%20to%20privatisation%20of%20the%20train%20paraphernalia.%20Instead%2C%20the%20basic%20thing%20required%20in%20the%20tendering%20process%20is%20that%20the%20minimum%20wages%20are%20ensured%3B%20the%20working%20hours%20are%20calculated%20and%20in%20case%20the%20period%20extends%20more%20than%20eight%20hours%20of%20work%2C%20double%20overtime%20is%20ensured%3B%20there%20is%20proper%20housing%20for%20the%20workers%20at%20their%20stations%20of%20boarding.%20This%20has%20been%20the%20practice%20since%20long%20and%20railway%20quarters%20were%20provided%20to%20the%20railway%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20since%20the%20workers%20are%20mobile%2C%20they%20require%20adequate%20housing%20for%20rest%20and%20other%20activities%20and%20cannot%20just%20be%20left%20out%20at%20the%20private%20workforce%20supplier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20railways%20should%20at%20least%20ensure%20proper%20and%20hygienic%20hostels%20if%20it%20cannot%20provide%20regular%20housing%20to%20this%20form%20of%20workforce%20so%20that%20they%20can%20rest%20and%20use%20their%20body%20to%20the%20best%20of%20their%20ability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20workers%20have%20finished%20their%20journey%2C%20there%20should%20be%20a%20rest%20day%2C%20the%20moment%20they%20cross%20more%20than%2016%20hours%20of%20work.%20It%20is%20humanly%20not%20possible%20for%20the%20workers%20to%20perform%20with%20the%20current%20model%20of%20working%20style.%20This%20affects%20their%20developmental%20process%2C%20both%20physical%20and%20psychological.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20railway%20ministry%20should%20regularly%20conduct%20health%20checkups%20of%20the%20workers%20and%20ensure%20that%20in%20the%20process%20of%20Vande%20Bharat%20glossy%20euphoria%20they%20are%20not%20destroying%20generations%20of%20young%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERailways%2C%20being%20the%20principal%20employer%20and%20controlled%20by%20the%20government%2C%20cannot%20run%20away%20from%20their%20constitutional%20duties%2C%20providing%20the%20right%20to%20life%20to%20every%20citizen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETikender%20Singh%20Panwar%20was%20once%20directly%20elected%20deputy%20mayor%20of%20Shimla.%20He%20was%20linked%20with%20the%20Leh%20Vision%20document%20and%20has%20written%20vision%20documents%20for%20a%20dozen%20cities.%20Author%20of%20two%20books%2C%20he%20is%20an%20urban%20specialist%20working%20in%20the%20design%20of%20inclusive%20cities.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709186250000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27161321%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-27-at-4.12.37-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fvande-bharat-and-the-treatment-of-its-service-providers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20much%20money%20is%20paid%20to%20the%20staff%3F%20How%20do%20they%20manage%20their%20rest%20or%20bodily%20requirements%3F%20Where%20do%20they%20take%20rest%20or%20sleep%3F%20Are%20they%20being%20provided%20with%20some%20social%20housing%20or%20hostels%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A140%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fvande-bharat-and-the-treatment-of-its-service-providers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22North%20Korea's%20arms%20factories%20are%20going%20full-tilt%20making%20weapons%20and%20ammo%20for%20Russia's%20war%2C%20says%20South%20Korea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226122%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20(R)%20and%20North%20Korean%20leader%20Kim%20Jong-un%20(L)%20visit%20a%20construction%20site%20of%20the%20Angara%20rocket%20launch%20complex%20on%20September%2013%2C%202023%20in%20Tsiolkovsky%2C%20Russia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e00a6bce7f1785b2e4d00d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224059%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20(R)%20and%20North%20Korean%20leader%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%20(L)%20visit%20a%20constr