3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMr.%20Narendran%2C%20who%20is%20a%20known%20person%20of%20our%20relatives%20took%20advantage%20of%20his%20introduction%20and%20came%20to%20me%20and%20sought%20for%20some%20amounts%20to%20the%20party%20in%20the%20centre%20which%20will%20be%20acknowledged%20by%20the%20way%20of%20bonds%2C%E2%80%9D%20Varma%20wrote%20in%20his%20complaint%20filed%20in%20Hyderabad%E2%80%99s%20Film%20Nagar%20police%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBelieving%20his%20words%2C%20my%20daughters%2C%20my%20wife%20have%20sent%20through%20bank%20to%20a%20total%20sum%20of%20Rs%202.5%20crores%20from%20time%20to%20time%20in%20the%20year%202021%20which%20can%20be%20seen%20from%20the%20text%20messages%20of%20%5BWhatsApp%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2072-year-old%20retired%20judge%2C%20who%20served%20in%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Allahabad%20high%20courts%2C%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftelangana%2Fformer-hc-judge-pays-rs-25-cr-to-rss-men-to-buy-electoral-bonds-gets-duped%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Verma%20mentioned%20that%20one%20of%20the%20two%20men%20he%20complained%20against%2C%20Anil%20(whose%20name%20was%20changed%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20the%20report)%2C%20was%20known%20to%20his%20son-in-law%20and%20they%20claimed%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98important%20leaders%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhumiliation-upending-poll-narratives-supreme-court-electoral-bonds-judgement%5C%22%3EHumiliation%20and%20the%20Upending%20of%20Poll%20Narratives%3A%20The%20Impact%20of%20the%20SC%E2%80%99s%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Judgment%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20report%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20Anil%E2%80%99s%20LinkedIn%20profile%20mentions%20that%20he%20is%20a%20coordinator%20for%20the%20World%20Hindu%20Congress%20and%20part%20of%20the%20World%20Hindu%20Economic%20Forum%2C%20an%20organisation%20that%20works%20closely%20with%20the%20RSS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Anil%20denied%20the%20judge%E2%80%99s%20claim%20and%20asserted%20that%20he%20has%20%E2%80%9Cno%20connections%20with%20RSS%20or%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20News%20Minute.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20complaint%2C%20Varma%20mentioned%20that%20the%20scammers%20claimed%20that%20they%20would%20purchase%20electoral%20bonds%20with%20the%20money%20and%20in%20exchange%20would%20%E2%80%9Cplace%20him%20and%20his%20grandchildren%20in%20%5Bthe%5D%20US%20decently%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20retired%20judge%20said%20that%20his%20two%20grandchildren%20have%20completed%20their%20postgraduate%20studies%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20common%20grievance%20of%20my%20family%20including%20me%20is%20that%20in%20spite%20of%20correcting%20%5Bcollecting%5D%20huge%20amounts%20no%20bonds%20have%20been%20issued%20to%20us%20in%20spite%20of%20my%20requests%2C%20nor%20any%20favour%20was%20done%20either%20to%20me%20or%20to%20my%20grand%20children%20in%20US%2C%20which%20is%20nor%20very%20relevant%20or%20significant%2C%E2%80%9D%20Varma%20wrote%20in%20the%20police%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20clear%20violation%20of%20the%20recent%20judgement%20of%20the%20supreme%20court%20deprecating%20the%20collection%20of%20amounts%20by%20way%20of%20electoral%20bounds.%20In%20the%20present%20case%20ispite%20%5Bin%20spite%5D%20of%20my%20insistence%20for%20issuing%20me%20bonds%20no%20such%20thing%20had%20happened.%20The%20said%20collection%20of%20amounts%20for%20about%202.5%20crores%2C%20with%20out%20issuing%20any%20bonds%20indicates%20that%20the%20said%20amounts%20was%20misappropriated%20for%20their%20self.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20the%20retired%20judge%20said%20that%20he%20paid%20everything%20in%20%E2%80%9Cwhite%E2%80%9D%20(legal%20money).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDespite%20asking%20several%20times%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20they%20did%20not%20issue%20the%20bonds%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20judge%20told%20the%20news%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709135304000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F08223208%2Frupee-g9dbf1131e_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felectoral-bonds-andhra-pradesh-high-court-retired-judge-scammed%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20his%20complaint%2C%20Varma%20mentioned%20that%20the%20scammers%20claimed%20that%20they%20would%20purchase%20electoral%20bonds%20with%20the%20money%20and%20in%20exchange%20they%20would%20%26quot%3Bplace%20him%20and%20his%20grandchildren%20in%20%5Bthe%5D%20US%20decently%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felectoral-bonds-andhra-pradesh-high-court-retired-judge-scammed%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Google%20hit%20with%20%242.3%20bn%20lawsuit%20by%2032%20media%20groups%20including%20Axel%20Springer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709133989000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-07%2F31%2Ffull%2F1690824463-9661.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgoogle-hit-with-2-3-bn-lawsuit-by-32-media-groups-including-axel-springer-124022801111_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20last%20year%20said%20it%20disagreed%20with%20EU%20antitrust%20charges%20against%20its%20ad%20tech%20business%20where%20it%20is%20involved%20in%20both%20the%20buy-side%20as%20well%20as%20the%20sell-side%20of%20the%20supply%20chain%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgoogle-hit-with-2-3-bn-lawsuit-by-32-media-groups-including-axel-springer-124022801111_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgoogle-hit-with-2-3-bn-lawsuit-by-32-media-groups-including-axel-springer-124022801111_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgoogle-hit-with-2-3-bn-lawsuit-by-32-media-groups-including-axel-springer-124022801111_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%202023%2C%20Over%20Two-Thirds%20of%20Hate%20Speech%20Against%20Muslims%20Was%20Made%20in%20BJP-Ruled%20States%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F14154412%2Fhate-speech.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Over%20two-thirds%20of%20hate%20speech%20events%20in%20India%20that%20targeted%20Muslims%20in%202023%20took%20place%20in%20BJP-ruled%20states%2C%20the%20research%20group%20India%20Hate%20Lab%20(IHL)%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIHL%20said%20it%20documented%20668%20such%20events%20during%202023%20and%20that%20453%20of%20these%20(68%25)%20took%20place%20in%20states%20ruled%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20%E2%80%93%20where%20police%20and%20law%20and%20order%20fall%20under%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20purview%20%E2%80%93%20and%20three%20Union%20territories%20accounted%20for%2045%20more%20hate%20speech%20events%20targeting%20Muslims.%20Thirty-seven%20of%20these%20occurred%20in%20the%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20states%20that%20saw%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20such%20hate%20speech%20events%20were%20Maharashtra%20(118)%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(104).%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20(68)%20was%20at%20a%20more%20distant%20third.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20three%20states%20accounted%20for%2043%25%20of%20all%20hate%20speech%20events%20in%20question%20for%202023%2C%20IHL%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20those%20responsible%20for%20organising%20these%20hate%20speech%20events%2C%20IHL%20said%20the%20Vishva%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP)%20and%20its%20youth%20wing%2C%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%2C%20had%20organised%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20events%20at%20216%20(32%25%20of%20the%20total).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second-most%20frequent%20organiser(s)%20of%20hate%20speech%20events%20were%20identified%20as%20Praveen%20Togadia%E2%80%99s%20Antarrashtriya%20Hindu%20Parishad%20and%20Rashtriya%20Bajrang%20Dal%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIHL%20said%20the%20BJP%20came%20in%20at%20third%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOrganisations%20%E2%80%9Cdirectly%20associated%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20Sangh%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20constellation%20of%20organisations%2C%20including%20the%20BJP%20and%20VHP%2C%20for%20which%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20is%20the%20ideological%20fountainhead%20%E2%80%93%20were%20behind%20307%20of%20the%20hate%20speech%20events%20in%20question%2C%20or%20about%2046%25%20of%20the%20total%2C%20IHL%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIHL%20also%20said%20it%20identified%20the%20speakers%20responsible%20for%20delivering%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20hate%20speech%20events.%20It%20said%20the%20far-right%20Hindu%20nationalist%20influencer%20Kajal%20Hindustani%20delivered%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20events%20at%2035%2C%20followed%20by%20Praveen%20Togadia%20(32)%20and%20the%20Maharashtra-based%20Dhananjay%20Desai%20(31).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelangana%20BJP%20MLA%20T.%20Raja%20Singh%20was%20in%20fifth%20place%20having%20delivered%2023%20hate%20speech%20events%2C%20IHL%E2%80%99s%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20its%20report%2C%20IHL%20has%20used%20the%20UN%E2%80%99s%20definition%20of%20hate%20speech%20to%20classify%20events%20it%20documented%20through%202023.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fen%2Fhate-speech%2Funderstanding-hate-speech%2Fwhat-is-hate-speech%5C%22%3EThe%20UN%20defines%20hate%20speech%20as%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAny%20kind%20of%20communication%20in%20speech%2C%20writing%20or%20behaviour%2C%20that%20attacks%20or%20uses%20pejorative%20or%20discriminatory%20language%20with%20reference%20to%20a%20person%20or%20a%20group%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20who%20they%20are%2C%20in%20other%20words%2C%20based%20on%20their%20religion%2C%20ethnicity%2C%20nationality%2C%20race%2C%20colour%2C%20descent%2C%20gender%20or%20other%20identity%20factor.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIHL%20highlighted%20that%20while%20hate%20speech%20is%20often%20characterised%20as%20extremists%20%E2%80%9Cventing%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Cbeing%20crazy%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20%E2%80%9Chas%20historically%20been%20understood%20to%20be%20an%20important%20causal%20factor%20in%20driving%20severe%20atrocities%20towards%20communities%2C%20including%20massacres%20and%20genocides%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20report%20also%20distinguishes%20%E2%80%9Cdangerous%20speech%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20subcategory%20of%20hate%20speech%20that%20involves%20a%20definite%20call%20for%20violence%20against%20target%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20239%20out%20of%20the%20668%20hate%20speech%20events%20under%20consideration%20(36%25)%20involved%20a%20direct%20call%20for%20violence%20against%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%2C%20the%20BJP%20MLA%20from%20Telangana%2C%20was%20identified%20as%20having%20delivered%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20dangerous%20speech%20events%20at%2014%2C%20and%20was%20followed%20by%20Togadia%20(ten)%20and%20Hindustani%20(nine).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20made%20communal%20remarks%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Ftelangana-bjp-mla-gives-provocative-speech-defies-bombay-hc-order%2Farticle67886258.ece%5C%22%3Eas%20recently%20as%20Sunday%20(February%2025)%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20railed%20against%20%E2%80%98love%20jihad%E2%80%99%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Mira%20Road%20and%20that%20the%20event%20featured%20songs%20%E2%80%9Ctargeting%20other%20religious%20groups%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELove%20jihad%20is%20a%20conspiracy%20theory%20supported%20by%20some%20Hindu%20nationalists%20in%20which%20Muslim%20men%20supposedly%20dupe%20unsuspecting%20Hindu%20girls%20into%20marriage%20in%20order%20to%20convert%20them%20to%20Islam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIHL%E2%80%99s%20report%20said%20that%20conspiracy%20theories%20such%20as%20love%20jihad%20were%20referred%20to%20in%20420%20(63%25)%20of%20the%20hate%20speech%20events%20in%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne-hundred-and-sixty-nine%20events%20(25%25)%20referenced%20Muslim%20places%20of%20worship%20and%20alleged%20they%20were%20built%20atop%20Hindu%20temples%2C%20the%20report%20added.%20Eighty-seven%20(13%25)%20called%20for%20a%20boycott%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2041%20events%20(21%25)%20used%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20to%20%E2%80%9Cfuel%20fear%20and%20animosity%E2%80%9D%20towards%20Indian%20Muslims%2C%20the%20report%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENuh%20violence%20%E2%80%98not%20spontaneous%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20included%20a%20case%20study%20of%20the%20Nuh%20riots%20that%20took%20place%20in%20July%20last%20year%20and%20said%20the%20incidents%20of%20violence%20%E2%80%9Cwere%20not%20spontaneous%20or%20organic%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CInstead%2C%20they%20were%20the%20result%20of%20a%20concerted%20effort%20by%20Hindu%20nationalist%20groups%2C%20over%20several%20months%2C%20to%20instigate%20violence%20in%20the%20region.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20started%20in%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20Nuh%20district%20on%20July%2031%20during%20a%20procession%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20VHP%20and%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal.%20By%20that%20evening%2C%20violent%20incidents%20were%20also%20reported%20in%20adjoining%20areas%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20people%20died%20and%20several%20others%20were%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIHL%20said%20the%20July%2031%20procession%20involved%20%E2%80%9Cseveral%20instances%E2%80%9D%20of%20hate%20speech.%20It%20also%20cited%20a%20%3Cem%3EHindutva%20Watch%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20as%20saying%20that%20the%20VHP%E2%80%99s%20president%2C%20Surendra%20Jain%2C%20delivered%20an%20%E2%80%9Can%20inflammatory%20speech%20against%20Muslims%E2%80%9D%20at%20Nuh%E2%80%99s%20Nalhar%20Mahadev%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20also%20reported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharyana-violence-mewat-hate-and-provocative-videos%5C%22%3Ehow%20provocative%20videos%20had%20preceded%20the%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Nuh.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709133852000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F14154412%2Fhate-speech.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Findia-hate-lab-hate-speech-against-muslims-2023-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20report%20by%20the%20India%20Hate%20Lab%20organisation%20also%20found%20that%20the%20Vishva%20Hindu%20Parishad%20and%20its%20youth%20wing%2C%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%2C%20organised%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20hate%20speech%20events%20targeting%20Muslims.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Findia-hate-lab-hate-speech-against-muslims-2023-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Taken%20for%20a%20Ride%E2%80%99%3A%20SC%20Issues%20Contempt%20Notice%20to%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%2C%20Its%20MD%20Over%20Misleading%20Ads%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F09164753%2Fpatanjali.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%