se%20all%20its%20%E2%80%9Cfalse%20and%20misleading%E2%80%9D%20advertisements.%20The%20top%20court%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmisleading-advertisements-fine-false-cure-claims-supreme-court-patanjali%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20any%20violation%20would%20result%20in%20an%20imposition%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%201%20crore%20on%20every%20product%20for%20which%20a%20false%20claim%20is%20made%20regarding%20its%20ability%20to%20cure%20a%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatanjali%20had%20then%20assured%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20it%20would%20not%20make%20statements%20against%20any%20system%20of%20medicine%2C%20or%20make%20any%20statements%20regarding%20the%20medical%20efficacy%20of%20Patanjali%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20continued%20to%20run%20such%20advertisements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%2C%20hence%2C%20issued%20contempt%20of%20court%20notices%20against%20Patanjali%20Ayurved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-issues-contempt-notice-to-patanjali-ayurved-its-md-for-misleading-ads-on-medicinal-cures-250636%5C%22%3E%20banned%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20company%20from%20running%20advertisements%20of%20products%20claiming%20to%20cure%20such%20diseases%2C%20%3Ci%3ELiveLaw%20%3C%2Fi%3Ereported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Govt%20sitting%20with%20its%20eyes%20closed%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98entire%20country%20was%20being%20taken%20for%20a%20ride%E2%80%99%20by%20such%20misleading%20advertisements.%20As%20earlier%20mentioned%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20also%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Union%20government%20for%20lack%20of%20action%20on%20the%20misleading%20advertisements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20is%20sitting%20with%20its%20eyes%20closed.%20This%20is%20very%20unfortunate.%20The%20government%20will%20have%20to%20take%20some%20immediate%20acti