20This%20makes%20it%20easier%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20engineer%20a%20collapse%20of%20the%20Congress%20government%20by%20mustering%20more%20number%20in%20the%20days%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20six%20defected%20MLAs%20were%20disqualified%20under%20anti-defection%2C%20as%20proceedings%20against%20them%20have%20already%20started%2C%20this%20would%20only%20bring%20down%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20existing%20strength%20of%2040%20MLAs%20in%20the%2068-member%20state%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20three%20senior%20Congress%20leaders%20have%20been%20sent%20to%20Shimla%20to%20douse%20the%20fire%2C%20the%20prevailing%20crisis%20evidently%20suggests%20that%20the%20leadership%20question%20has%20not%20fully%20settled%20in%20the%20party%20despite%20the%20high%20command-appointed%20Sukhu%20heading%20the%20government%20for%20almost%2015%20months%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20Congress%20rebels%20alleged%20that%20they%20were%20unhappy%20with%20Sukhu%E2%80%99s%20working%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20resignation%20of%20late%20Congress%20stalwart%20Virbhadra%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%2C%20from%20Sukhu%E2%80%99s%20cabinet%20escalated%20the%20ongoing%20crisis%20in%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirbhadra%2C%20an%20eight-time%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%2C%20passed%20away%20in%202021.%20The%20family%20believed%20that%20they%20were%20not%20given%20proper%20recognition%20even%20after%20the%20party%20won%20the%20assembly%20election%20in%202022%20on%20Virbhadra%E2%80%99s%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20late%20Virbhadra%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20Pratibha%20Singh%2C%20is%20currently%20the%20Himachal%20Congress%20chief%20even%20as%20the%20extreme%20crisis%20is%20unfolding%20in%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20survived%20budget%20session%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20defeating%20Congress%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20battle%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20game%20plan%20was%20to%20topple%20the%20Sukhu%20government%20by%20demanding%20division%20of%20votes%20before%20Wednesday%E2%80%99s%20%5BFebruary%2028%5D%20presentation%20of%20state%20budget%2C%20which%20is%20a%20customary%20practice%20whenever%20the%20ruling%20government%20presents%20financial%20Bills%20in%20the%20budget%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20nine%20MLAs%20cross-voted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20saffron%20party%20believed%20that%20the%20Congress%20no%20longer%20enjoyed%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20assembly%20and%20division%20of%20votes%20on%20financial%20Bills%20could%20collapse%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20delegation%2C%20under%20former%20chief%20minister%20Jai%20Ram%20Thakur%2C%20also%20met%20the%20Himachal%20governor%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20demanding%20a%20division%20of%20votes%20ahead%20of%20the%20budget%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20chaos%20reigned%20as%20the%20budget%20session%20was%20convened.%20Outmanoeuvering%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20assembly%20speaker%20suspended%20as%20many%20as%2015%20BJP%20MLAs%2C%20leading%20the%20remaining%2010%20MLAs%20to%20boycott%20the%20remaining%20house%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20the%20Sukhu%20government%20to%20pass%20the%20budget%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20opposition%20benches%20before%20the%20speaker%20declared%20the%20budget%20session%20sine%20die%20two%20days%20before%20the%20scheduled%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20Sukhu%20government%20too%20filed%20disqualification%20petitions%20against%20the%20Congress%20MLAs%20who%20voted%20for%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hearing%20for%20the%20same%20was%20held%20by%20the%20speaker%20but%20has%20remained%20inconclusive%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20session%2C%20Sukhu%20claimed%20that%20the%20budget%20was%20passed%20Wednesday%20and%20the%20conspiracy%20to%20topple%20his%20government%20by%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20foiled.%20%E2%80%9COur%20govt%20will%20complete%20five%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contrary%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Thakur%20claimed%20that%20the%20Congress%20had%20to%20suspend%20the%20BJP%20MLAs%20to%20save%20their%20government.%20But%20this%20government%20has%20lost%20the%20moral%20right%20to%20govern%20as%20it%20no%20longer%20enjoys%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20did%20not%20reveal%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20next%20course%20of%20action%2C%20other%20party%20leaders%20claimed%20that%20the%20Sukhu%20government%20is%20in%20for%20few%20days%20only.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20Harsh%20Mahajan%20%E2%80%93%20who%20won%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%20Tuesday%20against%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%20%E2%80%93%20told%20the%20media%2C%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20that%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20going%20to%20form%20its%20government%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20more%20Congress%20MLAs%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20us.%20The%20situation%20is%20going%20to%20change%20and%20you%20will%20see%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20form%20its%20government%20soon%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETug%20of%20war%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20top%20brass%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20jostling%20for%20power%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20top%20brass%20of%20both%20the%20parties%20are%20in%20a%20tug%20of%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi-Vadra%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20democracy%2C%20the%20public%20has%20the%20right%20to%20choose%20the%20government%20of%20their%20choice.%20The%20people%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20used%20this%20right%20and%20formed%20the%20Congress%20government%20with%20a%20clear%20majority.%20But%20BJP%20wants%20to%20crush%20this%20right%20of%20the%20people%20by%20misusing%20money%20power%2C%20power%20of%20agencies%20and%20power%20of%20the%20Centre.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarpal%20Cheema%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader%20and%20now%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20alliance%20partner%2C%20also%20told%20the%20media%20that%20the%20work%20of%20horse-trading%20of%20MLAs%20has%20now%20started%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20This%20is%20unfortunate%20for%20the%20country%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contrary%2C%20Union%20minister%20Anurag%20Thakur%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20formed%20the%20government%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20by%20giving%20big%20and%20fake%20promises.%20After%20the%20government%20was%20formed%2C%20none%20of%20those%20promises%20were%20fulfilled.%20People%20used%20to%20ask%20questions%20when%20Congress%20MLAs%20went%20to%20their%20constituencies%2C%20and%20they%20had%20no%20answers%20to%20give.%20That%20is%20why%20the%20Congress%20MLAs%20have%20started%20abandoning%20their%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Speaker%E2%80%99s%20action%20to%20disqualify%20the%20BJP%20MLAs%20during%20the%20budget%20session%2C%20Thakur%20said%20that%20what%20the%20Speaker%20did%20was%20inappropriate.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20numbers%2C%20and%20they%20themselves%20set%20the%20first%20example%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709129405000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F13215435%2FUntitled-design-9.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhimachal-pradeshs-congress-govt-survives-for-now-amid-defections-in-rajya-sabha%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20situation%20remains%20tense%20for%20the%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu-led%20government%2C%20as%20six%20defected%20Congress%20MLAs%20as%20well%20as%20three%20independents%20continue%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20the%20party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22http