%20vast%20expertise%20in%20their%20respective%20areas%20of%20work.%20Another%20science%20outreach%20organisation%2C%20the%20Indian%20Science%20Congress%20Association%20(ISCA)%20has%20been%20subjected%20to%20official%20apathy.%20The%20loss%20of%20these%20institutions%20will%20have%20far-reaching%20implications%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20scientific%20capabilities%20and%20global%20standing%20in%20the%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20speakers%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20pseudoscience%20endorsed%20by%20official%20agencies%20jeopardises%20public%20trust%20and%20undermines%20genuine%20scientific%20expertise%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEqually%20troubling%20is%20the%20promotion%20of%20pseudoscience%20over%20evidence-based%20research%20and%20established%20scientific%20principles.%20With%20a%20rise%20in%20the%20endorsement%20of%20unproven%20remedies%20and%20practices%20by%20official%20agencies%20and%20their%20funding%20by%20national%20research%20funding%20agencies%2C%20there%20is%20a%20risk%20of%20misleading%20the%20public%20and%20eroding%20trust%20in%20genuine%20scientific%20expertise.%20Such%20actions%20not%20only%20undermine%20public%20trust%20in%20science%2C%20and%20people%E2%80%99s%20health%20and%20safety%20but%20also%20jeopardize%20the%20credibility%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20scientific%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20said%20that%20bureaucratic%20delays%20in%20funding%20disbursement%20hamper%20research%20initiatives%2C%20while%20changes%20to%20school%20science%20syllabi%20prioritize%20ideological%20agendas%20over%20factual%20accuracy%2C%20hindering%20scientific%20literacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EReproduced%20below%20is%20the%20full%20statement.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStatement%20released%20by%20Scientists%20and%20Concerned%20Citizens%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%2C%20February%2026%2C%202024%3A%20Developments%20in%20recent%20years%20in%20India%20have%20caused%20concern%20within%20the%20scientific%20community%20and%20academic%20circles%2C%20pointing%20to%20a%20disconcerting%20trend%20of%20undermining%20scientific%20institutions%20and%20the%20constitutional%20idea%20of%20promoting%20scientific%20temper.%20From%20the%20abrupt%20closure%20of%20key%20institutions%20engaged%20in%20science%20communication%20to%20the%20promotion%20of%20pseudoscience%2C%20compounded%20by%20significant%20delays%20in%20the%20disbursement%20of%20funds%20and%20changes%20in%20school%20science%20syllabi%2C%20India%20is%20witnessing%20a%20systematic%20threat%20to%20its%20scientific%20foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20closure%20of%20Vigyan%20Prasar%20(VP)%2C%20which%20was%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20groundbreaking%20science%20communication%20and%20science%20popularisation%20efforts%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20merger%20of%20the%20National%20Institute%20for%20Science%2C%20Technology%20and%20Development%20Studies%20(NISTADS)%20with%20a%20new%20entity%2C%20seem%20to%20be%20directed%20at%20ending%20the%20only%20avenues%20of%20connecting%20science%20with%20society%20through%20well-informed%20channels.%20They%20were%20unique%20institutions%20in%20the%20developing%20world%20and%20had%20accumulated%20vast%20expertise%20in%20their%20respective%20areas%20of%20work.%20Another%20science%20outreach%20organisation%2C%20the%20Indian%20Science%20Congress%20Association%20(ISCA)%20has%20been%20subjected%20to%20official%20apathy.%20The%20loss%20of%20these%20institutions%20will%20have%20far-reaching%20implications%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20scientific%20capabilities%20and%20global%20standing%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEqually%20troubling%20is%20the%20promotion%20of%20pseudoscience%20over%20evidence-based%20research%20and%20established%20scientific%20principles.%20With%20a%20rise%20in%20the%20endorsement%20of%20unproven%20remedies%20and%20practices%20by%20official%20agencies%20and%20their%20funding%20by%20national%20research%20funding%20agencies%2C%20there%20is%20a%20risk%20of%20misleading%20the%20public%20and%20eroding%20trust%20in%20genuine%20scientific%20expertise.%20Such%20actions%20not%20only%20undermine%20public%20trust%20in%20science%2C%20and%20people%E2%80%99s%20health%20and%20safety%20but%20also%20jeopardize%20the%20credibility%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20scientific%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20bureaucratic%20delays%20in%20the%20disbursement%20of%20funds%20for%20scientific%20research%20projects%20and%20fellowships%20have%20left%20many%20young%20scientists%20and%20researchers%20in%20a%20precarious%20position.%20Without%20adequate%20funding%2C%20vital%20research%20initiatives%20are%20being%20hampered%2C%20leading%20to%20setbacks%20in%20critical%20areas.%20The%20decline%20in%20the%20budget%20allocated%20to%20science%20and%20higher%20education%20in%20general%2C%20and%20civilian%20R%26amp%3BD%20in%20particular%2C%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20does%20not%20augur%20well%20for%20Indian%20science%20as%20well%20as%20society.%20The%20continuous%20erosion%20of%20academic%20freedom%20is%20another%20matter%20of%20concern.%20All%20this%20could%20jeopardize%20India%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20address%20pressing%20societal%20challenges%20and%20capitalize%20on%20emerging%20opportunities%20using%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20these%20challenges%2C%20changes%20to%20school%20science%20syllabi%20have%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20quality%20and%20accuracy%20of%20science%20education%20in%20India.%20Alterations%20that%20prioritize%20ideological%20agendas%20over%20scientific%20facts%20risk%20hindering%20the%20development%20of%20a%20scientifically%20literate%20populace.%20This%20could%20have%20long-term%20implications%20for%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20foster%20a%20culture%20of%20innovation%20and%20critical%20thinking%20among%20its%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20advocates%20for%20evidence-based%20decision-making%20and%20scientific%20integrity%2C%20we%20feel%20that%20safeguarding%20scientific%20institutions%2C%20promoting%20rigorous%20research%20practices%2C%20ensuring%20timely%20funding%2C%20and%20upholding%20the%20integrity%20of%20science%20education%20are%20paramount%20to%20using%20science%20and%20technology%20for%20national%20development%2C%20and%20for%20the%20global%20competitiveness%20of%20Indian%20R%26amp%3BD.%20We%20urge%20the%20citizens%20to%20raise%20their%20voices%20against%20these%20disturbing%20trends.%20It%20is%20our%20constitutional%20duty%20to%20protect%20scientific%20institutions%20and%20promote%20scientific%20temper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EName%20Designation%20Affiliation%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEr.%20Anuj%20Sinha%20Former%20Scientist%20In-charge%20NCSTC%20(DST)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Director%20Vigyan%20Prasar%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Ashok%20Jain%20Former%20Director%20CSIR-NISTADS%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20D%20Raghunandan%2C%20Delhi%20Science%20Forum%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProf.%20Dinesh%20Abrol%20Former%20Chief%20Scientist%20CSIR-NISTADS%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Dinesh%20C%20Sharma%20Journalist%20%26amp%3B%20Author%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProf.%20Gauhar%20Raza%20Former%20Chief%20Scientist%20CSIR-NISCAIR%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Harshavardhana%20Hegde%20Orthopaedic%20Surgeon%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProf.%20Nandita%20Narain%20Former%20Head%20Mathematics%20Dept.%20Delhi%20University%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProf.%20N%20Raghuram%20GGSIU%2C%20Delhi%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERakesh%20Andania%2C%20Science%20Filmmaker%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Surjit%20Singh%2C%20Adjunct%20Prof.%20SIASTE%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ET%20V%20Venkateswaran%20Former%20Acting%20Director%20Vigyan%20Prasar%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709123520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28175801%2Fimage-1880.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdisconcerting-trend-over-the-undermining-of-scientific-institutions-threat-to-scientific-temper%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20group%20of%20former%20scientists%20and%20academicians%20have%20raised%20concerns%20over%20the%20abrupt%20closure%20of%20key%20institutions%20engaged%20in%20science%20communication%20to%20the%20promotion%20of%20pseudoscience%2C%20saying%20India%20is%20witnessing%20a%20systematic%20threat%20to%20its%20scientific%20foundation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdisconcerting-trend-over-the-undermining-of-scientific-institutions-threat-to-scientific-temper%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hate%20Speech%3A%20How%20to%20Promote%20Amity%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30123722%2FIllustration-Pariplab-Chakraborty.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20ruled%20by%20the%20Hindu%20nationalist%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20for%20the%20last%20decade.%20The%20BJP%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20is%20the%20progeny%20of%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%2C%20which%20has%20a%20goal%20of%20Hindu%20Rashtra.%20It%20has%20many%20progeny%2C%20hundreds%20of%20associated%20organisations%20with%20lakhs%20of%20volunteers%20(Swayamsevaks)%20and%20thousands%20of%20senior%20workers%20called%20Pracharaks%20(propagators).%20It%20has%20been%20pursuing%20its%20agenda%20of%20the%20Hindu%20nation%20with%20double%20the%20speed%20since%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20at%20the%20Centre.%20The%20rise%20of%20the%20BJP%20on%20electoral%20battlefield%20is%20due%20to%20intensifying%20of%20communal%20issues%2C%20Ram%20Temple%2C%20Cow-Beef%2C%20and%20Love-Jihad%20among%20others.%20Communal%20violence%20has%20been%20a%20major%20factor%20in%20increasing%20its%20electoral%20strength.%20The%20violence%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20is%20founded%20on%20%E2%80%98hate%20minorities%E2%80%99%20campaign.%20There%20are%20well-placed%20mechanisms%20to%20create%20hate%3A%20the%20chain%20of%20%3Cem%3Eshakhas%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20schools%2C%20Godi%20media%2C%20social%20media%20and%20IT%20cells%20among%20others.%20Hate%20speech%2C%20which%20is%20a%20punishable%20offense%2C%20is%20used%20with%20gay%20abandon%2C%20more%20so%20when%20the%20BJP%20is%20in%20power%20in%20states%20and%20also%20in%20Centre.%20Those%20indulging%20in%20hate%20speech%20do%20know%20that%20they%20enjoy%20a%20sort%20of%20impunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20this%20becomes%20ratified%20in%20the%20latest%20report%20released%20by%20%E2%80%98India%20Hate%20Lab%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20Washington%20DC-based%20group%20that%20documents%20hate%20speech%20against%20India%E2%80%99s%20religious%20minorities.%20The%20report%20with%20the%20title%20%E2%80%98Hate%20Speech%20Events%20in%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20notes%20that%20while%20255%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2F75-of-hate-speech-events-in-bjp-ruled-states-report%2Farticle67888978.ece%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2F75-of-hate-speech-events-in-bjp-ruled-states-report%2Farticle67888978.ece%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1709181335046000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0vwbazAAZLZ04ZbHVaL_J_%5C%22%3Eevents%20took%3C%2Fa%3E%20place%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%202023%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20number%20rose%20to%20413%20in%20the%20second%20half%20of%20the%20year%2C%20a%2062%25%20increase%E2%80%9D.%20The%20details%20are%20very%20revealing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20report%20nearly%2075%25%20of%20the%20events%20of%20the%20total%20(498)%2C%20took%20place%20in%20BJP-ruled%20states%2C%20Union%20territories%20(administered%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20Central%20government)%2C%20and%20Delhi%20(here%20police%20and%20public%20order%20come%20under%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20purview).%20While%2036%25%20(239)%20of%20the%20events%20%E2%80%9Cincluded%20a%20direct%20call%20of%20violence%20against%20Muslims%E2%80%9D%20and%2063%25%20(420)%20of%20incidents%20include%20references%20to%20%E2%80%9Cconspiracy%20theories%2C%20primarily%20involving%20love%20jihad%2C%20land%20jihad%2C%20and%20population%20jihad%E2%80%9D.%20About%2025%25%20(169)%20featured%20speeches%20calling%20for%20targeting%20Muslim%20places%20of%20worship.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resulting%20events%20are%20very%20well%20known%20by%20now.%20We%20remember%20the%20addition%20of%20the%20use%20of%20bulldozers%20and%20demolitions%20by%20BJP-ruled%20states.%20These%20are%20done%20mainly%20against%20the%20properties%20of%20Muslims.%20The%20demolition%20of%20the%20mosque%20here%20and%20there%20is%20no%20more%20a%20big%20deal.%20Boycotting%20Muslim%20hawkers%20and%20traders%20are%20occasionally%20propped%20up.%20Partiality%20done%20by%20the%20motivated%20administrative%20machinery%20is%20the%20order%20of%20the%20day.%20The%20impact%20on%20the%20Muslim%20community%20is%20an%20increasing%20sense%20of%20insecurity%20and%20ghettoization.%20The%20walls%20of%20Hatred%20are%20becoming%20stronger%20by%20the%20day.%20The%20hate%20speech%20signals%20begin%20from%20the%20top%20when%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20lately%20being%20called%20the%20reincarnation%20of%20Lord%20Vishnu%2C%20gives%20these%20hints%20like%2C%20that%20they%20can%20be%20identified%20with%20their%20clothes%2C%20Shamshan-Kabristan%20and%20Pink%20revolution.%20The%20next%20layer%20of%20hate%20spreaders%20further%20intensifies%20the%20language%20and%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Dharma%20Sansads%2C%20the%20holy%20ones%3B%20like%20Yati%20Narsinghnand%2C%20the%20message%20of%20violence%20becomes%20more%20direct%20and%20very%20despicable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F19160942%2Fpariplab.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F19160942%2Fpariplab.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F19160942%2Fpariplab-300x140.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-552976%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22478%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20peaks%20of%20this%20was%20witnessed%20in%20the%20parliament%20itself%20when%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20used%20expletives%20of%20the%20worst%20kind%20against%20Danish%20Ali%2C%C2%A0%C2%A0%E2%80%98Mullah%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98terrorist%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98anti-national%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98pimp%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ekatwa%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(a%20Hindi%20slur%20against%20Muslims).%20Bidhuri%20in%20turn%20was%20given%20additional%20promotion%20responsibility.%20This%20makes%20it%20clear%20the%20way%20of%20going%20in%20the%20upward%20direction%20of%20hierarchy%20in%20the%20BJP-RSS%20combine%20is%20hate%20speech.%20As%20Bidhuri%20was%20let%20off%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20by%20saying%20that%20if%20he%20repeats%20it%20again%2C%20action%20will%20be%20contemplated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20seen%20the%20horrific%20Bulli%20Bai%20and%20Sulli%20deals%20to%20humiliate%20prominent%20Muslim%20women%20and%20celebrities.%20The%20culprits%20went%20away%20without%20any%20serious%20punishments.%20Lately%20the%20Haldwani%20mosque%20issue%20also%20disturbed%20the%20peace%20at%20the%20ground%20level.%20The%20absence%20of%20an%20impartial%20media%20is%20the%20worst%20thing%20in%20the%20present%20scenario.%20The%20anchors%20of%20the%20big%20channels%20find%20the%20ways%20to%20blame%20the%20Muslims%20for%20every%20insinuation%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20leading%20to%20acts%20of%20violence%20against%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20the%20present%20trajectory%20of%20events%20is%20leading%20to%20gradually%20intensifying%20Islamophobia.%20We%20can%20see%20a%20teacher%20Tripta%20Tyagi%20asking%20the%20class%20students%20to%20slap%20a%20Muslim%20boy%20one%20by%20one%20for%20not%20doing%20homework.%20Another%20teacher%20Manjula%20Devi%20told%20two%20Muslim%20students%2C%20who%20were%20bickering%20over%20a%20minor%20issue%2C%20that%20this%20is%20not%20%E2%80%98their%20country%E2%80%99.%20We%20also%20witnessed%20a%20bus%20conductor%20Mohan%20Yadav%20being%20sacked%20as%20he%20stopped%20the%20bus%20for%20a%20brief%20while%20during%20which%20some%20passengers%20eased%20and%20a%20few%20Muslims%20offered%20Namaz%20during%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHate%20speech%20was%20identified%20by%20our%20leaders%20as%20a%20curse%20for%20our%20society.%20In%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20murder%20of%20Swami%20Sahajanand%20by%20a%20Muslim%2C%20Gandhi%20correctly%20identified%20the%20problem%20when%20he%20wrote%20in%20%3Cem%3EYoung%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20calling%20for%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6purging%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fgandhis-1926-call-for-boycott-of-newspapers-spreading-hatred-resonates-with-indias-decision%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fgandhis-1926-call-for-boycott-of-newspapers-spreading-hatred-resonates-with-indias-decision%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1709181335046000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0EAMyH0W2HG3CL_d0EesqW%5C%22%3Ethe%20atmosphere%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20mutual%20hatred%20and%20calumny%E2%80%9D%2C%20by%20%E2%80%9Cboycotting%20papers%20which%20foment%20hatred%20and%20spread%20misrepresentation%E2%80%9D.%20Here%20Gandhi%20is%20talking%20about%20the%20negative%20role%20of%20newspapers%20at%20that%20time.%20Later%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20murder%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20Golwalkar%20directly%20indicted%20RSS%20for%20spreading%20hatred%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20their%20speeches%20were%20full%20of%20communal%20poison.%20It%20was%20not%20necessary%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kractivist.org%2Fletter-sardar-vallabhai-patel-to-rss-chief-guru-golwalkar-1948-godse-mustread%2F%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.kractivist.org%2Fletter-sardar-vallabhai-patel-to-rss-chief-guru-golwalkar-1948-godse-mustread%2F%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1709181335046000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2bC3UscgA4pohaloOHDZcH%5C%22%3Eto%20spread%3C%2Fa%3E%20poison%20and%20enthuse%20the%20Hindus%20and%20organise%20for%20their%20protection.%20As%20a%20final%20result%20of%20the%20poison%2C%20the%20country%20had%20to%20suffer%20the%20sacrifice%20of%20the%20valuable%20life%20of%20Gandhi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clock%20has%20moved%20full%20circle.%20The%20same%20RSS%20has%20created%20layers%20and%20layers%20of%20hate-creating%20mechanisms.%20Apart%20from%20its%20own%20vast%20army%20of%20swayamsevaks%2C%20Pracharak%20and%20network%20of%20schools%2C%20a%20large%20section%20of%20media%20has%20totally%20surrendered%20to%20those%20in%20power%20and%20unabashedly%20using%20their%20influence%20to%20intensify%20hate.%20The%20social%20common%20sense%20created%20through%20these%20mechanisms%20leads%20to%20Bulli%20Bai%20and%20Sulli%20deals.%20It%20is%20this%20which%20creates%20Trupta%20Tyagi%20and%20Manjula%20Devi%20who%20take%20it%20to%20the%20young%20children.%20Things%20are%20becoming%20difficult%20for%20Muslim%20children%20in%20mixed%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20hate%20others%20has%20become%20the%20very%20antithesis%20of%20our%20constitution%E2%80%99s%20value%20of%20fraternity.%20It%20is%20also%20against%20the%20tolerance%20of%20the%20values%20of%20the%20morality%20of%20Hinduism%20as%20practiced%20by%20the%20likes%20of%20Gandhi.%20This%20is%20a%20very%20aggressive%20attack%20on%20the%20dictum%20of%20Vedas%2C%20%E2%80%98Vasudhaiva%20Kutumbkam%E2%80%99%20(World%20is%20a%20family)%2C%20this%20is%20not%20only%20intimidating%20the%20religious%20minorities%20it%20is%20an%20attack%20on%20t