343309%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJauzi%20Halwa%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ground%20Jauzi%20paste%20is%20then%20cooked%20with%20ghee%20(clarified%20butter)%2C%20sugar%2C%20milk%2C%20and%20aromatic%20spices%20such%20as%20cardamom%2C%20saffron%2C%20and%20nutmeg.%20In%20a%20food%20interview%20for%20Times%20Foodie%2C%20chef%20Ranveer%20Brar%20takes%20his%20guest%20to%20the%20iconic%20Hameedi%20confectionery%20to%20try%20the%20delicacy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E7.%20Haleem%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaleem%20is%20a%20savory%20and%20hearty%20stew%20that%20is%20immensely%20popular%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332569%2Fmohd-sujathullah-hyderabad-humanity-first-foundation-free-meals-for-poor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHyderabad%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20India%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%20The%20dish%20is%20made%20by%20slow-cooking%20a%20mixture%20of%20lentils%2C%20usually%20a%20combination%20of%20wheat%2C%20barley%2C%20and%20sometimes%20rice%2C%20along%20with%20meat%20(typically%20lamb%20or%20chicken)%2C%20until%20it%20reaches%20a%20thick%2C%20porridge-like%20consistency.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThis%20slow%20cooking%20process%2C%20often%20lasting%20several%20hours%2C%20allows%20the%20flavours%20to%20meld%20together%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20rich%20and%20velvety%20texture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20over%20hundreds%20of%20people%20visiting%20the%20place%20everyday%2C%20you%20should%20try%20Pista%20House%E2%80%99s%20haleem%20at%20least%20once%20in%20your%20life.%20Garnished%20with%20fried%20onions%2C%20fresh%20cilantro%2C%20mint%20leaves%2C%20and%20a%20squeeze%20of%20lemon%2C%20Pista%20House%20Haleem%20is%20a%20feast%20for%20the%20senses%2C%20captivating%20diners%20with%20its%20irresistible%20aroma%20and%20su