gaza-for-journalists-13082144%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98It%20Was%20My%20Mom%E2%80%99s%20Wish%E2%80%99%3A%20Woman%20Never%20Says%20No%20to%20Shelter%20Disabled%20%26amp%3B%20Abandoned%20Dogs%20at%20This%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20you%20define%20empathy%3F%20Can%20you%20find%20a%20semblance%20of%20solace%20in%20the%20service%20of%20sentient%20beings%20pushed%20to%20the%20margins%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20profound%20questions%20that%20Sarah%20Iyer%20%E2%80%94%20a%2058-year-old%20former%20special%20needs%20educator%20and%20founder%20of%20the%20Madras%20Animal%20Rescue%20Society%20(MARS)%20%E2%80%94%20has%20been%20answering%20with%20conviction%20for%20nearly%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20October%202019%2C%20the%20Chennai-based%20MARS%2C%20an%20animal%20welfare%20trust%20affiliated%20with%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Animal%20Welfare%20Board%2C%20has%20been%20running%20Daaman%20%E2%80%94%20a%20dog%20shelter%20situated%20along%20the%20East%20Coast%20Road%20(ECR)%20in%20Krishnan%20Karanai%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325192%2Fsaakshi-gulati-nikita-mathur-travel-with-kids-india-plan-vacations-for-moms-kids-toddlers-baby%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enear%20Mahabalipuram%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDaaman%20has%20over%20380%20dogs%20in%20their%20care%2C%20of%20which%2042%20are%20paraplegic%20puppies%20and%20more%20than%2050%20are%20either%20partially%20blind%2C%20blind%20or%20have%20neurological%20issues.%20The%20shelter%20is%20also%20home%20to%20more%20than%20100%20paraplegic%20adult%20dogs%20while%20the%20rest%20are%20old%2C%20abandoned%20and%20suffer%20from%20other%20disabilities.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBacked%20by%20six%20full-time%20staff%20members%20(all%20women)%2C%20Sarah%20and%20Gerry%20spend%20their%20days%20feeding%2C%20treating%2C%20rehabilitating%2C%20and%20caring%20for%20these%20forgotten%20creatures.%20Despite%20their%20abiding%20love%20for%20these%20dogs%2C%20it%20has%20not%20been%20an%20easy%20task.%20From%20offering%20lifelong%20care%20for%20these%20abandoned%20dogs%20to%20raising%20funds%20for%20them%2C%20these%20five%20years%20have%20been%20extremely%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Sarah%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COnce%20you%20see%20a%20video%20of%20a%20dog%20suffering%20or%20people%20ask%20you%20to%20rescue%20a%20dog%2C%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20say%20no.%20In%20most%20cases%2C%20the%20only%20option%20for%20old%2C%20blind%20or%20paraplegic%20dogs%20is%20euthanasia.%20Nobody%20will%20let%20them%20survive%20on%20the%20street.%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20live%20with%20the%20guilt%20of%20refusing%20shelter%20to%20a%20dog%20who%20needs%20it.%20I%20would%20rather%20see%20them%20alive%20than%20put%20down.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F6-2-1708958233.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dog%20Shelter%20and%20Home%20by%20MARS%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F6-2-1708958233.jpg%201920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F6-2-1708958233-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F6-2-1708958233-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F6-2-1708958233-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F6-2-1708958233-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F6-2-1708958233-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343230%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESarah%20Iyer%20feeding%2