Quality%20food%20makes%20a%20massive%20difference%20to%20these%20wounded%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDepending%20on%20their%20injury%20or%20health%20condition%2C%20we%20have%20to%20give%20them%20extra%20amounts%20of%20food.%20These%20dogs%20enter%20our%20shelter%20in%20a%20pathetic%20condition.%20What%20also%20takes%20up%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20our%20funds%20is%20the%20cost%20of%20medicine%20and%20regular%20check-ups.%20A%20lot%20of%20them%20get%20secondary%20infections.%20We%20also%20have%20old%20dogs%20with%20renal%20failure%20or%20enlarged%20livers%20or%20spleens.%20Another%20major%20hassle%20is%20managing%20tics%2C%20and%20buying%20quality%20medicine%20for%20it%20is%20also%20expensive.%20It%20also%20costs%20money%20to%20maintain%20these%20enclosures%20and%20the%20fencing%20surrounding%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20problem%20remains%20that%20the%20people%20who%20have%20brought%20some%20of%20these%20dogs%20to%20the%20shelter%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20take%20them%20back%2C%20and%20Sarah%20can%E2%80%99t%20put%20them%20back%20on%20the%20street.%20After%20six%20months%2C%20one%20can%E2%80%99t%20expect%20the%20dog%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20street.%20Given%20their%20territorial%20nature%2C%20the%20recovering%20pup%20or%20old%20dog%20will%20get%20attacked%20or%20chased%20down%20by%20other%20dogs%20on%20the%20streets%20who%20may%20not%20recognise%20it.%20Also%2C%20in%20the%20six%20months%20the%20dog%20has%20spent%20at%20the%20shelter%2C%20he%2Fshe%20has%20forgotten%20how%20to%20scavenge%20for%20food%20since%20they%20feed%20them%20regularly%20twice%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201057px)%20100vw%2C%201057px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSnapinsta.app_359730533_9487389331335803_6073002863132497370_n_1080-1708958805.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221057%5C%22%20alt%3D%