%20integrating%20tech%20into%20business%20and%20commercialising%20an%20idea%20for%20social%20impact.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20Akshay%20was%20selected%20for%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Agriculture%E2%80%99s%20RKVY-RAFTAAR%20Scheme%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338349%2Fhow-to-grow-saffron-with-aeroponics-online-classes-himachal-pradesh-solan-mushrooms%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edevelopment%20of%20agriculture%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20allied%20sectors.%20While%20the%20idea%20of%20biofertilisers%20had%20taken%20root%20in%20his%20mind%2C%20he%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20yet%20delved%20into%20the%20manufacturing%20process.%20But%20whilst%20at%20IITBHU%2C%20he%20recalls%20a%20seminar%20that%20helped%20him%20with%20his%20eureka%20moment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20observed%20that%20the%20processes%20of%20developing%20biofuel%20and%20biofertiliser%20were%20very%20similar.%20Both%20involve%20agricultural%20biomass%20being%20treated%20with%20microbes.%E2%80%9D%20Thus%20began%20the%20journey%20of%20Akshay%20and%20his%20mentor%20testing%20different%20kinds%20of%20microbes%20across%20farming%20lands%20for%20their%20characteristics%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20see%20which%20would%20work%20best%20when%20added%20to%20fertilisers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETowards%202020%2C%20Akshay%20had%20managed%20to%20come%20up%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338548%2Fmaharashtra-farmer-earns-huge-profits-by-growing-strawberry-farm-near-pune%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20set%20of%20biofertilisers%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20were%20all%20performing%20well.%20That%20same%20year%2C%20he%20formally%20launched%20LCB%20Fertilizers%20Pvt%20Ltd.%20But%20just%20when%20things%20were%20looking%20up%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20prepared%20microbe%20mixes%20in%20the%20laboratory%20and%20were%20in%20the%20process%20of%20testing%20the%20mixes%20on%20plants%20to%20check%20their%20efficiency.%20I%20had%20to%20return%20home%20with%20no%20idea%20of%20when%20I%20could%20get%20back%20to%20the%20lab.%20In%20the%20time%20that%20I%20was%20away%2C%20the%20microbe%20mixes%20had%20dried%20up%20and%20were%20now%20useless.%20I%20was%20back%20to%20square%20one%20%E2%80%94%20no%20lab%2C%20no%20money%20and%20no%20hope%20for%20what%20is%20next.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisappointment%20at%20having%20been%20so%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338048%2Fterrace-garden-tips-by-hyderabad-woman-grows-organic-vegetables-at-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclose%20to%20the%20dream%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20having%20to%20give%20up%2C%20clouded%20Akshay%E2%80%99s%20mind.%20During%20this%20time%20he%20was%20also%20offered%20a%20job%2C%20but%20a%20gut%20feeling%20told%20him%20he%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20give%20up%20on%20his%20dream%20just%20yet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20the%20next%20day%2C%20with%20a%20Rs%2010%2C000%20investment%2C%20Akshay%20decided%20to%20turn%20his%20shed%20outside%20his%20home%20into%20his%20lab.%20%E2%80%9CI%20purchased%20a%20pump%20from%20Amazon%2C%20a%20temperature%20sensor%20and%20I%20set%20up%20a%20bioreactor%20in%20my%20house.%20I%20had%20the%20know-how%20to%20prepare%20the%20fertiliser.%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20it%20at%20home.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20weeks%20that%20followed%2C%20Akshay%20went%20around%20collecting%20old%20wood%2C%20and%20soil%20from%20different%20types%20of%20environments%20%E2%80%94%20from%20harsh%20climates%2C%20marshy%20areas%20to%20loamy%20soil%20and%20cow%20dung.%20The%20first%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337129%2Feroponics-tower-planter-for-balcony-garden-by-iit-kanpur-startup-macrogardens%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebatch%20of%20fertiliser%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20prepared%20weighed%203%20kg.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-9-1708604729.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Navyakosh%20fertiliser%20bridges%20the%20gap%20between%20chemical%20and%20organic%20fertilisers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-9-1708604729.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-9-1708604729-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-9-1708604729-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-9-1708604729-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-9-1708604729-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342917%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Navyakosh%20fertiliser%20bridges%20the%20gap%20between%20chemical%20and%20organic%20fertilisers%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Akshay%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-10-1708605146.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20first%20production%20unit%20started%20by%20LCB%20Fertilizers%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-10-1708605146.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-10-1708605146-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-10-1708605146-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-10-1708605146-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-10-1708605146-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342918%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20production%20unit%20started%20by%20LCB%20Fertilizers%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Akshay%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkshay%20then%20proceeded%20to%20divide%20a%2012%20sq%20ft%20area%20outside%20the%20home%20into%20different%20portions.%20He%20planted%20seeds%20of%20carrots%2C%20spinach%20and%20radish%20in%20each%20portion%20but%20the%20choice%20of%20fertiliser%20was%20different%20%E2%80%94%20one%20batch%20was%20grown%20with%20a%20chemical%20fertiliser%2C%20one%20was%20grown%20with%20cow%20dung%2C%20one%20was%20grown%20with%20LCB%20fertiliser%20and%20the%20last%20with%20no%20fertiliser%20at%20all.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20you%20can%20guess%20which%20one%20thrived!%20Once%20the%20lockdown%20eased%20in%202021%2C%20Akshay%20approached%20IIT%20Kanpur%20where%20he%20met%20Dr%20Amitabha%20Bandopadhyay%20who%20helped%20him%20access%20labs%2C%20office%20space%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20a%20NIDHI%20Prayas%20Grant%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology%2C%20along%20with%20financial%20support%20of%20around%20Rs%208%20lakh%2C%20also%20boosted%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336832%2Fias-officer-sushant-gaurav-transforms-gumla-district-of-jharkhand-with-ragi-millet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproduct%E2%80%99s%20development%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0Akshay%20was%20joined%20by%20Mukesh%20Singh%2C%20Shubhendra%20and%20Raj%20Kamal%20in%20his%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20so%20special%20about%20this%20fertiliser%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20why%20crops%20seem%20to%20be%20loving%20the%20LCB%20fertiliser%2C%20Akshay%20says%20it%20is%20because%20it%20provides%20them%20with%20everything%20they%20were%20missing%20in%20other%20chemical%20and%20organic%20fertilisers.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSimply%20put%2C%20the%20fertiliser%20has%20four%20components.%20The%20first%20is%20a%20combination%20of%20microbes%20%E2%80%94%20nitrogen-fixing%2C%20potassium-mobilising%2C%20phosphorus-solubilising%2C%20and%20Trichoderma.%20This%20set%20helps%20the%20plant%20access%20the%20nutrients%20that%20it%20needs%20to%20grow%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20component%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336600%2Ftech-nursery-hydroponics-aeroponics-farming-ratlam-brothers-arbind-ravindra-dhakad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagricultural%20biomass%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20comprises%20seven%20types%20of%20biomass%20such%20as%20bagasse%2C%20cow%20dung%2C%20etc.%20The%20third%20component%20is%20the%20nanoparticles%20which%20increase%20the%20resistance%20of%20the%20microbes%20and%20help%20them%20survive%20in%20areas%20where%20it%20is%20hot.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20makes%20them%20thermophilic%20so%20that%20the%20microbes%20can%20survive%20at%20temperatures%20as%20high%20as%2070%20degrees%20celsius%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-11-1708605231.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Navyakosh%20fertiliser%20also%20helps%20farmers%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20times%20they%20irrigate%20the%20land%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-11-1708605231.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-11-1708605231-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-11-1708605231-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-11-1708605231-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-11-1708605231-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342919%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Navyakosh%20fertiliser%20also%20helps%20farmers%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20times%20they%20irrigate%20the%20land%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Akshay%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-12_11zon-1708605899.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20health%20of%20crops%20has%20visibly%20increased%20after%20farmers%20used%20the%20Navyakosh%20fertilisers%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-12_11zon-1708605899.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-12_11zon-1708605899-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-12_11zon-1708605899-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-12_11zon-1708605899-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-12_11zon-1708605899-150x79.j